        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post *This is a Weekly Price, Plus Tax No Lease, No Deposit, No Problem! Welcome to the Best Value in Extended-Stay Accommodations! With our all-inclusive pricing, you can pay weekly or monthly and save hundreds of dollars every month. Enjoy the convenience of no lease, no deposit, and no credit check for a hassle-free move-in experience. Your Safety is Our Priority: Our dedicated staff is on-site 24/7, and the property is key-controlled for your peace of mind. FREE Amenities Include: Under-bed storage for extra space and organizatio Secure property with key-controlled access Full Kitchens - Save $money$ by cooking your own meals Free Wi-Fi & Cable Free Utilities - Electric, A/C & Heat 24/7 on-site laundry faciliites Fully furnished, check-in ready studios No Lease - Check out on your schedule Flexible Payment Plans - Pay weekly or monthly Various Studio Layouts; Choose what's right for you! No Deposit - Check-in any time 24/7 vending machines with snacks and drinks All our rooms come with fully equipped kitchens, featuring dual stove-top burners, microwaves, full-size sinks, and refrigerators, so you can save even more on dining! Enjoy the convenience of on-site laundry available 24/7. We are also pet-friendly, welcoming up to two dogs under 50 lbs (pet fee applies). Book Your Stay Today! Experience the best value in WoodSpring Suites Tukwila! Limited-Time Offer for New Guests Only! Call: show contact info Pricing and availability are subject to change daily. Photos may not be of the exact advertised unit. Contact us today for the most up to date information. Extra charge for additional beds.",
