        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Come home to a great community - Quintessa Apartments! Address: 201 Yesler Way Seattle, WA 98104 Contact us for more information! show contact info Beds: 1 / Baths: 1 / Size: 525 sq ft Monthly Price: $1785 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Availability and pricing are subject to change daily Affordable housing in the heart of Pioneer Square! We are within walking distance of Pike's Place, Lumen Field, T-Mobile Park, and The Great Wheel Seattle. The main transit line is across from our building and King Street station is a few blocks away for all of your traveling needs. There are many restaurants, cafes, and art studios located in the area as well. We are a high-rise building, conveniently located in downtown, and our building offers great amenities! Enjoy our units with charming views of Puget Sound and downtown. A 24-hour gym is located on our main floor, as well as a common area to study, read, and relax. Make Quintessa your new home by calling us today to schedule a tour! Deposit: $400 Length of Lease: 12-Month Property Features: ● 24 Hour Availability ● Controlled building access ● Disposal Chutes ● Income Restricted ● Lounge ● Maintenance on site ● Video Patrol ● Across From Light Rail Station ● City Skyline Views ● Convenient To Everything ● Fitness Center ● Key Fob Entry ● Online Services ● Planned Social Activities ● Public Transportation ● Renters Insurance Program ● Subway within walking distance Apartment Amenities: ● Cable Ready ● Freezer ● Oven ● Smoke Free ● Tub/Shower ● Vinyl Flooring ● Air Conditioning ● Double Pane Windows ● Hardwood Floors ● High Speed Internet Access Pets: We welcome two pets per apartment home There is a $200 pet deposit per pet at move in. The monthly pet premium is $30. Please call the leasing office for our complete pet policy. $30 a month per pet 2 pet per home limit. Business Hours: Mon - Fri: 9:00 AM - 5:00 PM Ready to Lease? Contact us for more information! show contact info Website: www.apt-rental.com?n=quintessa&rp=aBHGtiutGy1X&t=wb Online Application: www.apt-rental.com?n=quintessa&rp=aBHGtiutGy1X&t=ap Schedule a Tour: www.apt-rental.com?n=quintessa&rp=aBHGtiutGy1X&t=sch 60% Income Limits: 1 - $66,00 2 - $75,420 3 - $84,840 4 - $94,260 5 - $101,820 6 - $109,380 7 - $116,940 8 - $124,440 80% Income Limits COMING IN JUNE: 1 - $88,000 2 - $100,560 3 - $113,120 4 - $125,680 5 - $135,760 6 - $145,840 7 - $155,920 8 - $165,920 All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY E0CA1D4C36B245",
