        "info": "QR Code Link to This Post -- Quintessa Apartments -- Call us today! show contact info Monthly Price: $1785 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Apartment: 1 Bedroom | 1 Bathroom Square Footage: 439 sq ft Availability and pricing are subject to change daily Affordable housing in the heart of Pioneer Square! We are within walking distance of Pike's Place, Lumen Field, T-Mobile Park, and The Great Wheel Seattle. The main transit line is across from our building and King Street station is a few blocks away for all of your traveling needs. There are many restaurants, cafes, and art studios located in the area as well. We are a high-rise building, conveniently located in downtown, and our building offers great amenities! Enjoy our units with charming views of Puget Sound and downtown. A 24-hour gym is located on our main floor, as well as a common area to study, read, and relax. Make Quintessa your new home by calling us today to schedule a tour! Pet Policy: We welcome two pets per apartment home There is a $200 pet deposit per pet at move in. The monthly pet premium is $30. Please call the leasing office for our complete pet policy. $30 a month per pet 2 pet per home limit. Check out our beautiful community featuring: ❖ 24 Hour Availability ❖ Controlled building access ❖ Disposal Chutes ❖ Income Restricted ❖ Lounge ❖ Maintenance on site ❖ Video Patrol ❖ Across From Light Rail Station ❖ City Skyline Views ❖ Convenient To Everything ❖ Fitness Center ❖ Key Fob Entry ❖ Online Services ❖ Planned Social Activities ❖ Public Transportation ❖ Renters Insurance Program ❖ Water Views Apartment features include: ❖ Cable Ready ❖ Freezer ❖ Oven ❖ Smoke Free ❖ Tub/Shower ❖ Vinyl Flooring ❖ Air Conditioning ❖ Double Pane Windows ❖ Hardwood Floors ❖ High Speed Internet Access Call us today! show contact info Mon - Fri: 9:00 AM - 5:00 PM Website: www.rentalsapts.com?n=quintessa&rp=7pSo4kvLPt5g&t=wb Online Application: www.rentalsapts.com?n=quintessa&rp=7pSo4kvLPt5g&t=ap Schedule a Tour: www.rentalsapts.com?n=quintessa&rp=7pSo4kvLPt5g&t=sch 201 Yesler Way Seattle, WA 98104 Lease Terms: 12-Month 60% Income Limits: 1 - $66,00 2 - $75,420 3 - $84,840 4 - $94,260 5 - $101,820 6 - $109,380 7 - $116,940 8 - $124,440 80% Income Limits COMING IN JUNE: 1 - $88,000 2 - $100,560 3 - $113,120 4 - $125,680 5 - $135,760 6 - $145,840 7 - $155,920 8 - $165,920 All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY 3CE6ED8E9D934E",
