        "geocode_query": "1321 Minor Ave",
        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Vesper Seattle redefines urban living in the Emerald City! Nestled in a lush pocket of tranquility on the border of Seattle’s Capitol Hill and First Hill neighborhoods, Vesper Seattle residents are steps away from chic shopping, dining and nightlife entertainment –not to mention, a hop, skip and jump from Downtown and the city’s breathtaking waterfront. Also nearby are major hospitals and business centers. Our prime location and abundant amenities achieve a difficult task: city-living in a park-like setting. Residents enjoy our state-of-the-art fitness center, ample covered parking, and the gorgeous panoramic views of the Seattle skyline and Olympic mountains from our rooftop terrace. Our thoughtfully designed one, two and three bedroom apartment homes each feature a washer-dryer unit, spacious floor plan, and modernized, fully equipped kitchen. Come, get inspired– call us to schedule a tour today! This apartment features: 8 – 14 Month Leases Available Enjoy spacious, cohesive layout Bright, open living room High ceiling, large bright windows! Open loft bedroom Large closets Ideal large private patio for warm summer months Fully-equipped kitchens with microwaves Convenient in home washer and dryer Garage parking available! Preferred floor levels available, ask us for details! Professional On-site Management Come Visit us! Vesper Apartments 1321 Minor Ave Seattle, WA 98101 https://livecreativejuices.com/k5b4jzpw/vesper-apartments Contact us today to schedule a tour! Call show contact info Office Hours Tuesday - Saturday 9:00 AM - 6:00 PM Closed Sunday & Monday Photos in ad may not be of actual apartment, however we try our best to use photos similar to the floor plan.",
