        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Come home to a great community - Sunrise Lane Apartment Homes! Address: 12522 8th Ave W Everett, WA 98204 Call us at show contact info Beds: 3 / Baths: 2 / Size: 1270 sq ft Monthly Price: $2350 - $2496 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Tucked away in the Westmont neighborhood, our gated community offers a peaceful retreat with easy access to everything you need. Choose from our spacious 1, 2, and 3-bedroom apartments, designed with open layouts, extra closet space, and classic finishes that make you feel right at home. Deposit: $400 Length of Lease: 6-Month, 7-Month, 8-Month, 9-Month, 10-Month, 11-Month, 12-Month $1000 Off Move-In Costs - Limited Time Special! Join us at Sunrise Lane! *Available on select homes for a limited time. Property Features: ✓ Business Center ✓ Controlled Access/Gated ✓ Fitness Center ✓ Garage ✓ More info on Garage ✓ Pet Friendly ✓ Playground ✓ Pool ✓ Recycling ✓ Spa/Hot Tub ✓ Availability 24 Hours ✓ Cabana/Gazebo ✓ Cardio Machines ✓ Coffee Station ✓ On-Site Management ✓ Outdoor Seasonal Heated Pool ✓ Picnic Area ✓ Resident Lounge ✓ Trash Pickup - Curbside ✓ Weight Machines Apartment Amenities: ✓ Dining Room ✓ Dishwasher ✓ Fireplace ✓ Linen Closet ✓ Pantry ✓ Patio/Balcony ✓ Smoke Free ✓ Walk-In Closets ✓ Washer/Dryer ✓ Baseboard Heat ✓ Energy Efficient Appliances ✓ Views Pets: Monthly Pet Rent: $50 per pet Deposit: $400 refundable deposit (for up to 2 pets) One-Time Fee: $200 non-refundable pet fee for 1st pet, $100 fee for 2nd pet Number of Pets: 2 pets per apartment home Weight Limit: No weight limit restrictions Age Restrictions: Dogs must be at least 6 months old Breed Restrictions: The following breed restrictions apply - Akita, Alaskan Malamute, Chow, Dalmatian, Doberman Pinscher, German Shepherd, Great Dane, Husky, Pit Bull Terriers*, Rottweiler, Saint Bernard, Wolf Dog Hybrids and all Pit Bull breeds (American 