        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post 3 Bed Room Beautiful apartments Leasing for Fall. Each unit has its own beautiful living space, kitchen, and newly renovated bathroom. Located in the highly desired U District community, 5-min Walk to the campus of University of Washington. 3-min Walk to U District Station of Seattle city train ( South to Seattle downtown, SeaTac Airport, North to Lynnwood and East to Bellevue and Redmond TechnoPark）. The building is located in the large commercial district surrounding the University of Washington. Excellent convenience for your transportation and daily life. This building has high-quality residents who are university teachers, college students, and technicians working in Seattle downtown, Bellevue, and Redmond TechnoPark. For more information and tour call or text show contact info Property Address: 4504 16th Ave NE, Seattle WA 98105 Please feel free to drive by and check out this wonderful apartmen",
