        "msg": "QR Code Link to This Post PREMIUM 4BR TOWNHOUSE IN CATHCART CROSSING TOP SCHOOLS & ZERO YARD WORK 14707 87th Ave SE, Unit BB8, Snohomish, WA 98296 Experience modern, stress-free luxury in the highly desirable Cathcart Crossing community. This spacious 4-bedroom \"Addison\" floor plan perfectly blends upscale living with an ideal commuter location and top-tier schools. WHY THIS HOME STANDS OUT: Perfect Commute: Direct access to WA-9 connects you smoothly to Hwy 522, I-405, and I-5 for an efficient drive to Bellevue, Redmond, and Seattle. Minutes to Essentials: Conveniently located just 5 minutes from Safeway, 10 minutes from Costco, and close to Mill Creek Town Center's dining and shopping. Top-Rated Schools: Zoned for the prestigious Snohomish School District (Cathcart Elementary, Valley View Middle, and Glacier Peak High School). True Maintenance-Free Living: The HOA fully covers all exterior and yard maintenance. Enjoy your weekends completely work-free. THE SPACE & LAYOUT: Ground Level: Features a rare guest ensuite with a full bath an ideal setup for a quiet home office, long-term guests, or a private teen retreat. Main Level: A bright, open-concept great room boasting soaring ceilings, expansive windows, a private deck, and a fenced yard. The chef's kitchen features a massive central island perfect for entertaining. Upper Level: A luxurious primary suite, two additional bedrooms, a full bath, and a dedicated utility/laundry room. Community Perks: Steps away from the neighborhood park and community pickleball courts. LEASE TERMS: Utilities: Tenant is responsible for all utilities (electric, water, sewer, and internet/cable). Move-In Requirements: First month's rent, last month's rent, and security deposit due at lease signing. Policies: No smoking.",
