        "msg": "QR Code Link to This Post Tucked away in a gated community, this inviting corner unit offers a private retreat with modern updates. Enjoy a secluded patio, fresh paint, brand-new carpeting, and an updated kitchen with stainless steel appliances and a newly installed water heater. The spacious layout provides a comfortable and functional living space, perfect for relaxing or entertaining. Residents enjoy unmatched amenities, including a secluded lake, athletic courts, exercise room, scenic trails, 4 outdoor pools, sauna, clubhouse, private cocktail lounge, game room, and community pea patches. Complete with a private carport and storage, this home blends comfort and convenience in a prime location—just minutes from Downtown Redmond, Kirkland, and Bellevue.",
