        "msg": "QR Code Link to This Post Welcome Home To Sherwood Gardens! Sherwood Gardens is a beautiful and friendly park-like apartment community that offers comfortable living at affordable prices. The beautiful Sherwood Gardens grounds include a playground, pool and picnic area. Residents can choose from one and two bedroom apartment layouts, completed with amenities such as all-electric kitchen, ceiling fans, walk-in closets, kitchen pantry, and more! This apartment features: Great Value for Location! 3-D VIRTUAL TOUR Available!  Ask us for more info! Open concept living room Plenty of natural light Fully-equipped kitchen with Dishwasher, Microwave Wood Flooring On-site laundry facility Courtyard & pool view Generous walk-in closets Parking space included Professional On-site Management Photos in ad may not be of actual apartment, however we try our best to use photos similar to the floor plan. Come Visit us! Sherwood Gardens 2901 Auburn Way S Auburn, WA 98092 https://livecreativejuices.com/sptolofy/sherwood-gardens Contact us today to schedule a tour! Call show contact info Office Hours Tuesday – Friday 9:00am – 6:00pm Saturday 10:00am – 4:00pm Closed Sunday and Monday Photos in ad may not be of actual apartment, however we try our best to use photos similar to the floor plan.",
