        "msg": "QR Code Link to This Post 🌟 LIMITED-TIME COLOSSAL SPECIAL! 🌟 Move-In Special Available Now Take advantage of this exclusive offer when you apply and move in between June 1st - June 5th! 28620 Pacific Hwy S, Federal Way, WA 98003 Welcome to La Madera! La Madera is an affordable housing property located in Federal Way, WA that features spacious Studio, 1, 2 & 3 bedroom apartments in a beautiful community setting. Units were recently renovated in 2023! La Madera is an income restricted property. Applicants must meet income requirements to qualify for homes at La Madera. There is a $42 application fee per adult. Residents at La Madera enjoy the convenient location the property offers. La Madera is a close distance away from local restaurants, grocery stores, shopping centers, city parks and lakes, and the Federal Way School District. There is so much to do and experience in the area! Come in and see our professional management team today, they would love to show you around. Schedule a tour today! 🏠 Available Units & Pricing Studio Apartment 💲 $999/month 🎉 + 2 Months FREE Rent 1-Bedroom Apartment 💲 $1,299/month 🎉 + 2 Months FREE Rent 2-Bedroom Apartment 💲 $1,550/month 🎉 + 2 Months FREE Rent 💰 BIG SAVINGS Enjoy up to $8,020 in total savings when you sign a 6-month lease! Features Include: Bicycle Storage On-site Parking Renovated in 2023 Internet Access Oven Electric Range Playground Large Closets Cable TV Access Professional Management Bike Storage Heat (Electric) Call: show contact info For more information, visit us at: https://livecascademgmt.com/trfcuggc/la-madera We are pledged to the letter and spirit of U.S. policy for the achievement of equal housing opportunity throughout the Nation. We encourage and support an affirmative advertising and marketing program in which there are no barriers to obtaining housing because of race, color, religion, sex, handicap, familial status, or national origin. Application fee of $42 per adult. Pricing and availability are subject to change daily. Photos may not be of the exact advertised unit. Contact us today for the most up to date information.",
