        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Welcome home to this cozy first-floor condo in a secure, gated community! With 1 bedroom, 1 bathroom, and 680 sq ft of thoughtfully designed living space, you’ll appreciate the open-concept layout that’s ready for your personal style. The dining area connects effortlessly to the living room, where a cozy gas fireplace sets the tone for relaxing evenings. Step outside to your private patio, ideal for a quiet morning coffee or casual entertaining. Conveniently located near shopping, dining, schools, Boeing, I-5, and even a golf course just blocks away. Your designated parking spot means no hunting for a space, and with water, sewer, garbage, and common area upkeep included in the HOA, life here stays refreshingly low-maintenance.",
