        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Woodhaven 4632 Fowler Ave Everett, WA 98203 Monthly Price: $1800 - $2018 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Bedrooms: 2 Bathrooms: 1 Square Footage: 850 sq ft Call us: show contact info Features in this apartment home: ◾ Carpeting ◾ Ceiling Fans ◾ Heating ◾ Linen Closet ◾ Oven ◾ Patio/Balcony in Most Units ◾ Range ◾ Refrigerator ◾ Smoke Free ◾ Tub/Shower ◾ Built-in Bookshelves ◾ Cable Ready ◾ Crown Molding ◾ Dishwasher ◾ Double Pane Windows ◾ Faux Wood Flooring ◾ Granite Countertops ◾ Upgraded Interiors ◾ Vinyl Flooring ◾ Window Covering About the community: Our pet-friendly community provides everything that you need to live the life that you deserve. From the playground to the BBQ and pet park, every community amenity has been designed to evoke a strong sense of community and provide an escape from the stress of day-to-day life. So leave all your worries at the door because the comforts and convenience of our community spaces extend to all our one, two, and three-bedroom apartments for rent in Everett. Each apartment home has modern amenities such as faux wood flooring, patios/balconies, and ceiling fans to create that warm, inviting feeling. Amenities at our property: ◾ 24 Hour Maintenance ◾ BBQ/Picnic Area ◾ Beautiful Landscaping ◾ Community Garden ◾ Cornhole ◾ Courtyard ◾ Laundry Facilities ◾ Off Street Parking ◾ Online Services ◾ Easy Access to Historic Downtown Everett ◾ Minutes from Everett Naval Station ◾ Pet Friendly ◾ Pet Play Area ◾ Playground ◾ Property Manager on Site ◾ Renters Insurance Program ◾ Secluded Forest Park Location ◾ Shuffleboard ◾ Storage Units for Rent Additional information: Call us: show contact info Terms: 6-Month, 8-Month, 9-Month, 10-Month, 12-Month Pets: 2 pets per apartment home $50 pet rent per pet $400 deposit per pet $200 non-refundable deposit for 1st pet, $250 for additional pet The following breed restrictions apply - Akita, Alaskan Malamute, Chow, Dalmatian, Doberman Pinscher, German Shepherd, Great Dane, Husky, Rottweiler, Saint Bernard, Wolf Dog Hybrids and all Pit Bull breeds. Website: www.apts-rental.com?n=woodhaven&rp=uJ2JwcueMAwe&t=wb Online Application: www.apts-rental.com?n=woodhaven&rp=uJ2JwcueMAwe&t=ap 3D Virtual Tour: www.apts-rental.com?n=woodhaven&rp=uJ2JwcueMAwe&t=trt Schedule a Tour: www.apts-rental.com?n=woodhaven&rp=uJ2JwcueMAwe&t=sch All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY 6866967C5B3149B",
