        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Bedrooms:  2 Bathrooms:  2 Square Feet:  908 Date Available:  2026-06-18 Address:  1324 Mill Creek Blvd Discover a sanctuary nestled amidst nature at The Ardent, offering idyllic living in our newly remodeled* one and two-bedroom residences. Surrounded by expansive, protected walking trails and a preserved natural haven, our community provides a tranquil escape from the hustle while keeping you near the vibrant pulse of Mill Creek Town Center’s shopping and dining experiences. The Ardent is not merely a residence—it’s a paw-approved retreat where luxury intertwines with comfort in our beautiful apartment homes, while also boasting a wide array of resort-inspired amenities. From trying your hand at tennis, to swimming laps in our refreshing pool, to hosting an event in our lively gaming and recreation room, everything you need is at your fingertips. Immerse yourself in a home where the beauty of your surroundings amplifies a lifestyle replete with leisure and comfort. All applicants are subject to standard screening criteria and program requirements. Housing Choice Voucher applicants are welcome to apply! Amenities Include: In Home Stackable Washer/Dryer Tennis Court Guest Parking Pet-friendly Community Basketball Court Entertainment and Lounge Areas Bark Park & Pet Grooming Studio Fully-equipped Kitchen with Stainless Steel Appliances Outdoor Playground Granite Countertops Call: show contact info For more information, visit us at: https://livewithtopaz.com/t5c4n4wx/ardent-at-mill-creek *Pricing and availability are subject to change daily. Photos may not be of the exact advertised unit. Contact us today for the most up to date information.",
