        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Villa Apartments Leasing Office: 1106 Pike St Seattle, WA 98101 Office Phone: show contact info Take a look at what Villa Apartments has to offer! Villa Apartments in Seattle is ready for your visit. Be sure to check out the current floorplan options. The professional leasing team is ready and waiting for you to visit. Villa Apartments features a variety of amenities including: instant hot water, door to door trash pick-up, and curbside trash pick-up. Contact us or drop by to schedule your tour and make your move to Villa Apartments. Rental Information: Studio Bedroom / 1 Bathroom / 458 sq ft Monthly Price: $1150 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Lease Terms: 12-Month Apartment Amenities: Additional Information: ● Classic building ● Controlled access ● Elevator ● On-site laundry ● Pet friendly ● Pet Play Area ● Shared courtyard ● Community amenities coming soon! ● Paid parking available (Please inquire for availability and cost) ● Paid water/sewer/garbage ● Property Manager on Site ● Resident Services available ● Retail or restaurants in building ● Section 8 vouchers accepted ● Trash Pickup - Curbside Leasing Hours: Mon - Sun: - Office Phone: show contact info Pet Policy: Pets as well as emotional support, companion, and service animals are allowed in all Community Roots Housing buildings. Some restrictions may apply to certain types of pets. Site managers can answer detailed questions about pet restrictions. Website: www.leaseaptsnow.com?n=villa&rp=mUxhRZGj6z2Q&t=wb Online Application: www.leaseaptsnow.com?n=villa&rp=mUxhRZGj6z2Q&t=ap All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY 82RKXLXSBZCMBIB3",
