        "info": "QR Code Link to This Post Beds: 1 Baths: 1 Square Feet: 615 We're committed to helping you find your next home! Follow the below link to contact us. https://olympic.touraptnow.com/1t2a1v Welcome to Benson Village Call Now - show contact info x 215 OR Text 215 to show contact info to contact our team.   Community Info Thanks for checking out Benson Village Apartments. We are a locally owned and professionally managed community in Kent, WA. Benson Village is conveniently located near the ShoWare Center, Kent Station Movie Theater, Dave and Buster's, iFly Indoor Skydiving and a multitude of shopping and dining options. We have 1- & 2-bedroom apartments and 3- & 4-bedroom townhomes. Our newly renovated apartment homes are a great value, featuring spacious floor plans with energy efficient appliances and lighting, plank flooring, linen closet and additional storage space off the patio or balcony. Select units are fully renovated and include stainless steel appliances. We have a community clubhouse with featured monthly events, basketball, racquetball and tennis courts, fitness center and tanning bed. Residence Features ✩  Fully Renovated* ✩  Walk - In Closet* ✩  Solid Surface Countertops ✩  Patio / Balcony ✩  In - Unit Laundry* ✩  Plank Flooring ✩  Spacious Floor Plans ✩  Full Size W/D* ✩  Storage Space ✩  Energy Efficient Appliances ✩  Energy Efficient LED Lighting ✩  Stainless Steel Appliances* Community Features ✩  On - Site Management ✩  Basketball Court ✩  Laundry Facility ✩  24 - Hour Emergency Maintenance ✩  Racquetball Court ✩  Tennis Court ✩  Community Clubhouse ✩  Fitness Center ✩  Playground Office Hours Monday-Friday: 9:00AM-6:00PM Saturday-Sunday: 10:00AM-5:00PM Equal Housing Opportunity AxA7n5NG0",
