        "info": "QR Code Link to This Post The Orion Address: 29 St. Helens Ave Tacoma, WA 98402 Monthly Price: $1567 - $1682 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Bedrooms: 1 | Baths: 1 | Sq. Footage: 525 sq ft | Terms: 6-Month, 7-Month, 8-Month, 9-Month, 10-Month, 11-Month, 12-Month Call Today! show contact info + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + Features in this apartment home: ● 1 and 2 Bedroom Apartment Homes and Penthouses ● 16 Floors of Spectacular Views of Commencement Bay* ● Cable Ready ● Elevator(s) ● Fully-equipped Kitchen ● High Speed Internet Access ● Oven/Range ● Refrigerator/Freezer ● Window Coverings ● Wood-look Plank Flooring ● 16 Floors of Spectacular Views of Commencement Bay in Select Units ● Electronic Thermostat ● Heating ● Large Closets ● Stainless Steel Appliances ● Views ● Wood-look Plank Flooring + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + Amenities at our property: ● 24-Hour Clothes Care Center ● Business Center/Clubhouse/Gameroom ● Elevator ● Laundry Facilities ● Outdoor Patios & Grill Station ● Pet Waste Stations ● Recycling ● Renters Insurance Program ● Smoke Free ● Sundeck ● 1,500 Sq. Foot Residential Lounge with Stunning Views & Complimentary Wi-Fi ● 24-Hour On-site Emergency Maintenance ● Bocce Ball Court ● Immediate Access to Wright Park and Seymour Conservatory - Voted \"Best Place to Relax\" in Tacoma ● Online Services ● Package Service ● Planned Social Activities ● Rentable Storage is Available in the Community with Varying Sizes ● Waterfront ● Yoga Studio + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + About the community: Located in the heart of Tacoma's Stadium District, Orion is a newly renovated high-rise community offering 1 & 2 bedroom apartments and penthouses with panoramic views of Mt. Rainier, Puget Sound, Wright Park, and the desirable New Tacoma city lights. Enjoy living in the \"#1 most walkable\" district in Tacoma with nearly 200 restaurants, bars, coffee shops, and local parks nearby. Orion also offers convenient access to Tacoma Link Light Rail and 705/I-5. Pets: Pet policy: We are pet friendly! Both dogs and cats are allowed! Pets - Max 2 Allowed Pet Deposit: $250 per pet One-time Pet Fee: $250 per pet Monthly Pet Rent: $35 per pet We do not have a weight limit. Call Today! show contact info Hours: Mon - Fri: 9:00 AM - 6:00 PM Website: www.lease-apts.com?n=orion&rp=oZJUq2ne4HQ4&t=wb Online Application: www.lease-apts.com?n=orion&rp=oZJUq2ne4HQ4&t=ap Schedule a Tour: www.lease-apts.com?n=orion&rp=oZJUq2ne4HQ4&t=sch Availability and pricing are subject to change daily All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY 5Z2X8A2ERXKBOL",
