        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Welcome to The Ridge at Bellevue Rental Information Monthly Price: $1950 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. 1 Bedroom 1 Bath | 660 sq ft Lease Term: 12-Month Call our office at show contact info Apartment Amenities ➢ Hardwood Floors ➢ High Speed Internet Access ➢ Quartz Countertops-*select units ➢ Refrigerator ➢ Stainless Steel Appliances-*select units ➢ Vinyl Flooring ➢ Washer/Dryer-*select units ➢ Wheelchair Accessible (Rooms) ➢ Window Coverings Community Features ➢ Carport ➢ Courtyard ➢ Elevator ➢ Gated ➢ Picnic Area ➢ Storage Space ➢ Carport ➢ Courtyard ➢ Elevator ➢ Picnic Area ➢ Storage Space About Community Description: Set in the lively Crossroads neighborhood, our apartments in Bellevue, WA, put you in the center of it all. Major roads like I-405, N 8th St, and 148 Ave make commuting a breeze, whether you're heading to Redmond's tech hub, Downtown Seattle, or beyond. Top employers - including Intellectual Ventures, Valve, and Overlake Medical Center - are just minutes away, while Bellevue College, the University of Washington, and DigiPen Institute of Technology ensure top-tier education is always close. Need a break? Explore Kelsey Creek Park, the Botanical Garden, or Chism Beach Park, or enjoy shopping and dining at Crossroads Mall and Bellevue Square. Whatever your day looks like, we keep you near everything that matters. Location: 13831 NE 8th St Bellevue, WA 98005 show contact info Office Hours: Mon - Fri: 9:00 AM - 6:00 PM Saturday-Sunday : By Appointment Additional Information Call our office at show contact info Pet Policy: We are a pet friendly community! Permitted Animals: Domestic cats, fish (aquarium limit: 50 gallons), birds, and dogs. Prohibited Dog Breeds: Akita, Alaskan Malamute, Chow Chow, Doberman, German Shepherd, Great Dane, Pit Bull, Rottweiler, Saint Bernard, Shar Pei, Siberian Husky, and any mix thereof. 2 pets per household. No weight limit Prohibited Animals: Snakes, ferrets, iguanas, rabbits, potbelly pigs, insects, and other exotic or wild animals. Fees: A non-refundable pet fee of $250, additional monthly rent of $35 per pet, and an additional deposit may be required. Al Website: www.rentalsapts.com?n=ridge_at_bellevue&rp=fWKHcoXxpTTr&t=wb Online Application: www.rentalsapts.com?n=ridge_at_bellevue&rp=fWKHcoXxpTTr&t=ap Schedule a Tour: www.rentalsapts.com?n=ridge_at_bellevue&rp=fWKHcoXxpTTr&t=sch All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY BJGZK4RHELCMC4MJ",
