        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Highlands West Shoreline - A place to call home! Bed: 1 / Bath: 1 Sq. Footage: 750 sq ft Monthly Price: $1900 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Terms: 12-Month Contact our leasing office at show contact info Nestled on the shores of Puget Sound, Seattle is home to glorious mountain views in the distance, making it one of the most scenic metropolitan areas in the nation. Skyscrapers like the Columbia Center and Space Needle grace the city's skyline, adding to Seattle's allure. Starbucks, Amazon, and Nordstrom have headquarters in Seattle, so there are plenty of job opportunities in the city. Interstates 5 and 405 and the Seattle-Tacoma International Airport are major benefits for frequent travelers. Residents enjoy exploring the waterfront neighborhoods of Pioneer Square and the famous Pike Place Market for shopping, trendy bars, and restaurants. Enjoy the peace of the Richmond Beach area is quiet 55 Plus Community. Walking distance to grocery shopping, local restaurants and a short 10 minute drive to Richmond Beach itself. Highlands & Highlands West Apartments are just a great place to live. Call today or stop by to schedule a tour. Our Apartment Homes Feature: ● Dishwasher ● Extra Large Windows ● Freezer ● Heating ● Kitchen ● Oven ● Pantry ● Range ● Refrigerator ● Smoke Free Our Residents Enjoy: ● Access to Exercise Room ● Beautiful Landscaping ● Community Room ● Large Screen TV ● Maintenance Emergency on-call ● On-site Office Staff ● Public Parks Nearby ● Set in a Garden Setting with Koi Pond ● Shimmering Swimming Pool ● Smoke-free Community Contact our leasing office at show contact info 18520 8th Ave NW Shoreline, WA 98177 Website: www.leaseaptsnow.com?n=highlands_west_shoreline&rp=nHQ35jFiikut&t=wb Online Application: www.leaseaptsnow.com?n=highlands_west_shoreline&rp=nHQ35jFiikut&t=ap Schedule a Tour: www.leaseaptsnow.com?n=highlands_wes