        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post 1 Bedroom 1 Bathroom | 699 sq ft Monthly Price: $1950 - $2099 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Sunset Terrace 2715 Sunset Ln NE Renton, WA 98056 Contact: show contact info Description: Sunset Terrace is located at 2715 Sunset Ln NE Renton, WA. Sunset Terrace offers Studio to 2-bedroom apartments ranging in size from 456 to 1206 sq.ft. This apartment community is pet friendly, welcoming both cats and dogs. Discover Your Perfect Home: Schedule an Appointment for a Tour Today! Apartment Amenities: ✓ Dishwasher ✓ Disposal ✓ High Speed Internet Access ✓ Microwave ✓ Quartz Countertops ✓ Smoke Free ✓ Stainless Steel Appliances ✓ Vinyl Flooring ✓ Walk In Closets ✓ Walk-In Closets ✓ Air conditioning ports for portable unit ✓ Choose from light or dark interior scheme ✓ Convenient in-unit washer and dryer ✓ Juliette balconies/Private patios ✓ Kitchen islands with pendant lighting ✓ Pantry closets ✓ Quartz countertops and satin nickel hardware ✓ Under cabinet lighting ✓ Wired for easy cable-ready connection Our Residents Enjoy: ✓ Business Center ✓ Clubhouse ✓ EV Charging ✓ Fitness Center ✓ Key Fob Entry ✓ Lounge ✓ Multi Use Room ✓ On-Site Retail ✓ Package Service ✓ Recycling ✓ Built-in pet wash ✓ Cycling hub with substantial bike parking ✓ EV car chargers ✓ Gas Firepit ✓ Park and mountain views ✓ Professional on-site management and maintenance ✓ Secure entry with video access calling ✓ Secure package lockers ✓ Trash chute and eco-conscious recycling room ✓ Welcoming lobby with fireplace and soft seating Additional Details: Deposit: Call Terms: 6-Month, 7-Month, 8-Month, 9-Month, 10-Month, 11-Month, 12-Month Pets: Please see Pets page for more details! Contact: show contact info Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/LiveSunsetTerrace/ Website: www.apt-rental.com?n=sunset_terrace&rp=hfaS3kd6pRLa&t=wb Online Application: www.apt-rental.com?n=sunset_terrace&rp=