        "msg": "QR Code Link to This Post RENTAL INFO Monthly Price: $2050- $2649 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. The Trail Apartments: 627 Avenue A Snohomish, WA 98290 Apartment for Rent: 1 - 3-BR 1 - 2-BA | Square Feet: 625 - 1140 sq ft | Lease Length: Variable Contact us for more information! show contact info PROPERTY AMENITIES ● Accepts Electronic Payments ● Barbecue Area ● Basketball Court ● Covered Parking ● Online Leasing ● On-Line Payments ● Pet Friendly ● Playground ● Recycling ● Storage ● Ideal Location in Snohomish ● Near Restaurants and Shops ● On-Site Maintenance ● On-Site Management APARTMENT AMENITIES ● Cable Ready ● Dishwasher ● Hard Surface Flooring in Living and Dining Areas ● Patio/Balcony ● Quartz Counters ● Spacious Living Areas ● Updated Kitchen ● Vinyl Flooring ● Washer/Dryer ● Window Coverings ADDITIONAL INFO Description: \"Currently fully leased. Accepting inquiries for future available units.\" The Trail is located in an ideal location in Snohomish, WA. Situated next to the Interurban Trail and the Snohomish Aquatic Center Recreational Park, residents enjoy easy access to local amenities in a quiet neighborhood setting. Enjoy walking or biking to parks, restaurants or shops, or a quick jaunt to nearby downtown Snohomish for historical flavor and antiques shopping. Our one-, two- and three-bedroom floor plans feature modern, spacious living areas and a private patio or balcony. As a resident, you'll enjoy the central playground area with plenty of room to run. We offer carports and extra storage units for your convenience. An ideal location, and many great amenities, make The Trail Apartments the perfect place to call home. Pet Policy: 2 pets per apartment home No weight limit $50 pet rent per pet $400 refundable deposit, $200 pet fee ($300 for 2 pets) The following breed restrictions apply - Akita, Alaskan Malamute, Chow, Dalmatian, Doberman Pinscher, German Shepherd, Great Dane, Husky, Rottweiler, Saint Bernard, Wolf Dog Hybrids and all Pit Bull breeds. Website: www.lease-apts.com?n=trail&rp=fTRzZ5P43sM4&t=wb 3D Virtual Tour: www.lease-apts.com?n=trail&rp=fTRzZ5P43sM4&t=trt Schedule a Tour: www.lease-apts.com?n=trail&rp=fTRzZ5P43sM4&t=sch Contact us for more information! show contact info Photos are representational only. Actual home may have small changes. All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY N3MEDI0TDB86Z05E",
