        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Foster Commons Call Today! show contact info Spring time Special_ Act now! Limited Availability This won't last long! Offering one month free on a 12-month lease. Reach out to our team for more details. Restrictions apply, offer valid on select homes. Apartment Details: 2-BR 1-BA | Square Footage: 864 sq ft Monthly Price: $1850 - $1975 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Lease Length: 6-Month, 12-Month Apartment Features: ● Balcony or Patio ● Cable Ready ● Carpeted Floors ● Carport Available ● Ceiling Fans ● Dishwasher ● Efficient Appliances ● Extra Storage ● Fireplace ● Garbage Disposal ● Greenbelt Views* ● Modern Kitchen ● Personal Storage ● Refrigerator ● Self Cleaning Oven ● Spacious Closets ● USB Outlets ● Washer & Dryer in Unit ● White Appliances ● Wood burning fireplace About Our Community: We strive to create a welcoming atmosphere where each of our residents truly feels at home. Prepare to be captivated by our one and two bedroom apartments for rent with exceptional amenities, including an in-home washer and dryer, additional storage space, generously sized closets, and a contemporary kitchen equipped with a dishwasher to save valuable time. Unwind on your balcony or patio, taking in the night sky, and then cozy up next to the fireplace for a delightful evening of warmth and relaxation. Your satisfaction is our top priority at Foster Commons in Seattle, Washington. Pet Policy: Pets Welcome Upon Approval. Deposit: $225 Refundable and $225 Non-Refundable Pet Fee $20 per pet per month Breed restrictions apply. Limit of 2 pets per home. 35 lbs. weight restrictions Wonderful Amenities: ● 24-Hour Availability ● Accepts Electronic Payments ● Carports ● Off Street Parking ● On-Site Maintenance ● On-Site Property Manager ● Pet Friendly ● Public Transportation ● Section 8 Vouchers Accepted ● Tranquil Outdoors ● Easy Access to Freeways Garden Style ● Emergency Maintenance ● Guest Parking ● King County - Housing Vouchers Welcome ● Large Dogs Allowed ● Mail Locker ● Night Patrol ● On-line Maintenance Request Contact Information: Address: 5700 S 129th Street Seattle, WA 98178 Call Today! show contact info Website: www.apts-rental.com?n=foster_commons&rp=3cELBj6f7Ek4&t=wb Online Application: www.apts-rental.com?n=foster_commons&rp=3cELBj6f7Ek4&t=ap Schedule a Tour: www.apts-rental.com?n=foster_commons&rp=3cELBj6f7Ek4&t=sch All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY 52VK5OMH1ZIS1N2A",
