        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Village on Main Apartments 5020 Main St Ruston, WA 98407 A wonderful home in Ruston is waiting for you! Call us today! show contact info We currently have a gorgeous 3 bedroom 2 bathroom with 1219 sq ft. Monthly Price: $3650 - $3701 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Each apartment home offers wood-style plank flooring, polished quartz countertops, expansive bay windows, and 9-foot ceilings - plus so much more! These luxe interiors offer the utmost living experience Tacoma has to offer. $1500 off your move in!! Community Highlights: − Along the Point Ruston Waterwalk − Bike storage − Controlled-entry access − Landscaped courtyard with outdoor seating − Pet friendly − State-of-the-art fitness center − 50 onsite retail with unique eateries and shopping right at your doorstep − Package locker with 24/7 access to packages − Private parking garage with direct access elevators − Resident social lounge with demonstration kitchen and pool table − Virtual Moving Concierge: Complimentary address change, set up home services and digital moving announcements − Worry-free 24-hour onsite maintenance Apartment Home Highlights: − 9-foot ceilings − Elevator access − Furnished apartments available − In-home washer and dryer − Oversized walk-in closets − Private balcony or patio − Separate dining area − Wood-style plank flooring − Air conditioning with programmable remote thermostat − Breakfast bar with pendant lighting − Expansive bay windows with 2-inch wood blinds − Income Qualified Apartment Home (MFTE) − Panoramic views of South Puget Sound, the Olympic Mountains, and Mount Rainier − Polished kitchen countertops − Stainless steel appliances including built-in microwave, refrigerator, and dishwasher Call us today! show contact info Website: www.leaseaptsnow.com?n=village_on_main&rp=77zpWTjyuKNQ&t=wb Online Application: www.leaseaptsnow.com?n=village_on_main&rp=77zpWTjyuKNQ&t=ap Leasing Options: 3-Month, 4-Month, 5-Month, 6-Month, 7-Month, 8-Month, 9-Month, 10-Month, 11-Month, 12-Month, 13-Month Pet Policy: Dogs and cats are welcome at our community. All pet residents must have their health check, shots and be spayed or neutered upon move-in. A signed Animal Addendum is required to be on file at our leasing office. Two (2) max pets allowed and breed restriction! We only rent our apartments directly through our website or leasing office. We do not use any electronic funds transferring apps such as Zelle, Venmo, or Cashapp. All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY D287E1686AA04B4",
