        "geocode_query": "1721 Fircrest Dr SE",
        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post RENTAL INFO Monthly Price: $1140 - $1140 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Conifer Ridge: 1721 Fircrest Dr SE Port Orchard, WA 98366 Apartment for Rent: 1-BR 1-BA | Square Feet: 550 - 550 sq ft | Lease Length: 12-Month Call: show contact info PROPERTY AMENITIES ➢ Community Room ➢ Handicap Accessible Units Available ➢ Landlord pays water, sewer, garbage. Tenant pays electric. Very reasonable electricity cost. ➢ Laundry Facilities ➢ Lift/Elevator ➢ Non-Smoking Property ➢ Professionally Landscaped ➢ Secure Entrance to Building ➢ Smoke Free ➢ Within Para-Transit Route APARTMENT AMENITIES ➢ ADA Units Available ➢ Additional Storage ➢ Balcony/Patio ➢ Cable Ready ➢ Carpet ➢ Heating ➢ High Speed Internet Access ➢ Refrigerator ➢ Stove/Range ADDITIONAL INFO Description: \"Currently fully leased. Accepting inquiries for future available units.\" HOUSING FOR SENIORS 62+ OR DISABLED Conifer Ridge is designed for seniors 62+ years or persons with disabilities. All of our units are one bedroom units with 3 units being ADA accessible. We are close to shopping and recreation and a Meals on Wheels for Seniors Nutrition Program. Pet Policy: No Pets Website: www.leaseaptsnow.com?n=conifer_ridge&rp=jTGjved7QYMP&t=wb Call: show contact info Housing for seniors 62 or older or disabled. This property offers subsidy for 32 out of 40 units through the USDA Rental Assistance program. With this subsidy your rent will be based on 30% of your income. Non-subsidized units have a base rent that you will pay. If subsidy is not available at move-in, your rent will not be subsidized. However. once a tenant, if qualified for subsidy, your household will be placed on a wait list for subsidy based on greatest financial need. We also accept housing authority provided Section 8 vouchers. All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY 6VL7R12GS827CVZ",
