      "house_ger": {
        "id": "8fb0ebe0-a763-44b0-a434-763c0dd93a81",
        "name": "Amplify your life: 1 BR, 1 BA, and tons of space!",
        "location": "12333 120th Ave NE",
        "mainpic": "5cad7178-7448-4d49-81d1-2d1071b5c942",
        "msg": "QR Code Link to This Post 1 Bedroom 1 Bathroom | 586 sq ft Monthly Price: $1703 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Polaris at Totem Lake 12333 120th Ave NE Kirkland, WA 98034 Contact Info: show contact info Description: Discover the heart of community living at Polaris at Totem Lake in Kirkland, WA. Here, neighbors become friends and shared spaces-from inviting resident lounges to thoughtfully designed outdoor areas-are created to bring people together. With a warm, welcoming atmosphere and a true sense of connection, Polaris at Totem Lake sets the stage for meaningful moments and everyday comfort. Whether you're hosting a casual weekend gathering or enjoying a peaceful walk around the neighborhood, this is a place where you can truly feel at home. Come be a part of something special. Your community awaits. Apartment Amenities: ➢ Clubhouse ➢ Freezer ➢ Gameroom ➢ Gated ➢ Grill ➢ Kitchen ➢ Microwave ➢ Oven ➢ Playground ➢ Smoke Free ➢ Bicycle Storage ➢ Meal Service ➢ Media Center/Movie Theatre ➢ Online Services ➢ Property Manager on Site ➢ Quartz Countertops ➢ Recreation Room ➢ Refrigerator ➢ Vinyl Flooring ➢ Washer/Dryer Our Residents Enjoy: ➢ Close to shopping ➢ Elevator ➢ Enclosed Courtyard ➢ Game Room ➢ Interior Playground ➢ Movie Theater ➢ Online Rent Payments ➢ Pet Friendly ➢ Access to public Transportation ➢ Non-Smoking Community ➢ Online Maintenance Portal ➢ On-site Bike Storage ➢ Parking: $150/month Max 1 parking space with limited availability ➢ Picnic Area with BBQ ➢ Some Paid Utilities: Water, Sewer, and Garbage ➢ State-of-the-art Fitness Center Additional Details: Deposit: Call Terms: 6-Month Pets: Pet policy: We are pet friendly! Both dogs and cats are allowed! Pets - Max 2 Allowed Refundable Pet Deposit: $250 per household Monthly Pet Rent: $25 per pet The following breed restrictions apply: Pit Bull, Rottweiler, Presa Canario, German Shepherd, Husky, Malamute, Doberman, Chow Chow, St. Bernard, Great Dane, Akita, Staffordshire Terriers, American Bull Dog, Karelian Bear Dog. Exotic Animals: Reptiles, Ferrets, Skunks, Raccoons, Squirrels, Rabbits, Birds, Pigs, Arachnids, Piranha, other farm or poisonous animals. Aquarium max 5 gallons, must be on the first floor, Manage We are an income restricted community. Check our Eligibility tab for information regarding rental criteria Contact Info: show contact info Website: www.apt-rental.com?n=polaris_at_totem_lake&rp=iJ9F3Ngk1a4E&t=wb Online Application: www.apt-rental.com?n=polaris_at_totem_lake&rp=iJ9F3Ngk1a4E&t=ap 3D Virtual Tour: www.apt-rental.com?n=polaris_at_totem_lake&rp=iJ9F3Ngk1a4E&t=trt Schedule a Tour: www.apt-rental.com?n=polaris_at_totem_lake&rp=iJ9F3Ngk1a4E&t=sch All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY GSVZAVXS52SOEIA6",
