        "info": "QR Code Link to This Post Elizabeth Thomas Homes Leasing Office: 4524 S. Henderson St. Seattle, WA 98118 show contact info Take a look at what Elizabeth Thomas Homes has to offer! Affordable housing conveniently located near light rail station! Experience unparalleled comfort and convenience at Elizabeth Thomas Homes, a newly constructed affordable housing community located in the Rainier Beach neighborhood of Seattle, WA. Each of our energy-efficient studio, 1-bedroom, 2-bedroom & 3-bedroom apartment homes was meticulously designed to showcase contemporary and stylish interiors with top-notch finishes and fixtures. Our residents also enjoy a remarkable selection of community amenities such as a gated front entry leading to a spacious courtyard and playground area, a community lounge with a large smart TV, and a computer lab with 6 computers and a printer. **Income restrictions apply. Income Restrictions for Elizabeth Thomas Homes # Occupants - Max Income 1 Person - $55,000 1 Person - $66,000 2 People - $62,850 2 People - $75,420 3 People - $70,700 3 People - $84,840 4 People - $78,550 4 People - $94,840 5 People - $84,850 5 People - $101,820 To qualify, the combined annual gross income of a household must be below the maximum annual income amounts listed in the chart. Maximum income limits are based on whether the apartment is a 50% or 60% AMI unit and on the total number of people who will be living in the home. Experience unparalleled comfort and convenience at Elizabeth Thomas Homes, an Affordable Housing Community where a remarkable range of apartment features awaits residents! Our 1-bedroom, 1-bathroom apartment homes are energy efficient, spacious, and thoughtfully crafted to optimize natural light. With convenient access to public transportation, commuting becomes effortless, allowing you to explore the vibrant city and beyond. The clubhouse provides a perfect space for socializing and hosting gatherings, while disability access ensures inclusivity and convenience for all residents. Income Restrictions for Elizabeth Thomas Homes # Occupants - Max Income 1 Person - $55,000 1 Person - $66,000 2 People - $62,850 2 People - $75,420 3 People - $70,700 3 People - $84,840 4 People - $78,550 4 People - $94,260 5 People - $84,850 5 People - $101,820 To qualify, the combined annual gross income of a household must be below the maximum annual income amounts listed in the chart. Maximum income limits are based on whether the apartment is a 50% or 60% AMI unit and on the total number of people who will be living in the home. Rental Information: 1 Bedroom / 1 Bathroom / 486 sq ft Monthly Price: $1644 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Apartment Amenities: ◾ Dishwasher ◾ Energy Efficient Appliances ◾ Energy-Efficient Windows ◾ Oven ◾ Vinyl Flooring Additional Information: ◾ Affordable Housing ◾ Bike Storage ◾ Community Laundry Room ◾ Computer Lab ◾ Controlled Access ◾ Income Restrictions Apply ◾ New Construction ◾ On-line Maintenance Request ◾ Section 42 Welcome ◾ Smoke Free ◾ 24/7 Resident Portal for Work Orders, Payments & Communicating with the office! ◾ Community room for events, parties etc. ◾ Computer Lab with designated Resident Printer ◾ One block from Rainier Beach light rail station ◾ Rooftop deck with views ◾ Walking distance to schools, grocery, community centers Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/share/1EHgcSwpGz/ Income Restrictions for Elizabeth Thomas Homes # Occupants   -   Max Income       1 Person   -   $63,240       5 People   -   $97,680       2 People   -   $72,300       6 People   -   $104,940       3 People   -   $81,360       7 People   -   $112,080       4 People   -   $90,420       8 People   -   $119,340 To qualify, the combined annual gross (before deductions) income of a household must be below a specific amount. Maximum income limits are based on whether the apartment is a 50% or 60% AMI unit and on the total number of people who will be living in the home. Please contact our friendly Team for more information! Online Application: www.leaseaptsnow.com?n=elizabeth_thomas&rp=1gLx4m2dDFuj&t=ap Website: www.leaseaptsnow.com?n=elizabeth_thomas&rp=1gLx4m2dDFuj&t=wb Elizabeth Thomas Homes is an Affordable Housing Community participating in the Low-Income Housing Tax Credit (LIHTC) Program, with both 50% and 60% AMI apartment homes. All applicants aged 18 years of age or older must complete their own application and pass our application screening criteria. We must also verify that each household meets all program requirements before they can be approved for move-in by verifying the income, assets, and student statuses for all occupants. Property information, pricing and income limits are current as of 03/15/2025. Rental rates, income limits, unit availability, lease terms, deposits, apartment features, amenities and specials are subject to change without notice. Terms may fluctuate based on qualifying standards. Floorplans and square footages displayed are approximations, and may vary between individual units. Occupancy guidelines may apply, unless otherwise specified. Pricing is valid for new residents only. Please contact the leasing office for more details. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY E07D50F2E01E444",
