        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Latitude 112 - A place to call home! Bed: 3 / Bath: 2 Sq. Footage: 1155 sq ft Monthly Price: $2373 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Terms: 12-Month Call Today! show contact info Latitude 112 apartments in Seattle, Washington is under new management. Imagine retreating to your beautiful new apartment home, where every room invites you to stay a while. Our spacious one, two, and three-bedroom floor plans are thoughtfully designed for a stylish and comfortable feel. Featuring sleek cabinet design, efficient appliances, and hard surface flooring punctuate modern apartment living in Seattle, WA You'll have access to various premium amenities-whether you're watching a movie in our theater, shooting hoops on the basketball court, or staying active in the fitness center. We're also pet-friendly, so your furry companions can enjoy the comforts of your new home alongside you. With all the ways Latitude 112 apartments in Seattle, Washington can enhance your lifestyle and still be affordable; why wait? Call today to schedule a tour! Spring Special! - 6 weeks free on one bedroom floor plans with a 12- month lease term. Restrictions apply. Reach out to our team for more details. Offer Valid on select units. Our Apartment Homes Feature: − Built-in Microwave − Central Heat − Dishwasher − Efficient Appliances − Hard Surface Flooring − Microwave − Business Center − Fitness Center − Playground − Spacious Floor plans − Two-tone Cabinets − Washer and Dryer in Every Home − Washer and Dryer in Home Our Residents Enjoy: − Basketball Court − Billiards Room − Business Center − Elevator − Fitness Center − Non-smoking − Pet-friendly − Playground − Playgrounds − Theater Room − Dishwasher − Microwave − Washer and Dryer in Home Call Today! show contact info 125 SW 112th Street Seattle, WA 98146 Website: www.apt-rental.com?n=latitude_112&rp=n61dbYdp4r5y&t=wb Online Application: www.apt-rental.com?n=latitude_112&rp=n61dbYdp4r5y&t=ap Schedule a Tour: www.apt-rental.com?n=latitude_112&rp=n61dbYdp4r5y&t=sch Mon - Fri: 9:00 AM - 5:00 PM Pets: Pet Welcome Upon Approval. Breed restrictions apply. Limit of 2 pets per home. Non-refundable pet fee is $200 per pet. Pet deposit is $200 per pet. Monthly pet rent of $25 will be charged per pet *The availability of certain amenities may be affected by ongoing preventative maintenance and necessary repair work. All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY 7CSRMOXM2N2GLXN",
