        "info": "QR Code Link to This Post Studio Bedroom 1 Bathroom | 546 - 768 sq ft Monthly Price: $2293 - $2395 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. The Stadium Apartments 102 N G St Tacoma, WA 98403 Call our office at show contact info Description: Finding your perfect apartment just got a whole lot easier-and way more exciting. Picture yourself in a stunning one, or two-bedroom home with sleek, contemporary design, high-end finishes, and floor plans that flex to fit your lifestyle. This isn't just a place to live-it's a space to thrive. Located in one of the city's most coveted neighborhoods, you're not just upgrading your address-you're elevating your entire way of living. Apartment Amenities: ◾ Dishwasher ◾ Disposal ◾ Efficient Appliances ◾ Electronic Thermostat ◾ Extra Storage ◾ Ice Maker ◾ Microwave ◾ Refrigerator ◾ Wheelchair Access ◾ Air Conditioner Portal for Free Standing Units ◾ Full Size Front Load Stacked Washer/Dryer ◾ Fully Furnished Units Available ◾ High Ceilings on 1st and 7th floor ◾ Large Closets and Walk-In's on Select Units ◾ Large Patio's and Balconies in Select Units. ◾ Views of Commencement Bay, Wright Park, Mt. Rainier/Cascades/Olympics, and Stadium High School Our Residents Enjoy: ◾ 24 Hour Availability ◾ Community Room ◾ Courtyard ◾ Dog Park ◾ Electric Car Stations ◾ Elevator ◾ Fitness Center ◾ Recycling ◾ Roof Terrace ◾ Storage ◾ Air Conditioner Portal for Free Standing Units ◾ Efficient Appliances ◾ Electronic Thermostat ◾ Full Size Front Load Stacked Washer/Dryer ◾ Fully Furnished Units Available ◾ Large Patio's and Balconies ◾ Multi Use Room ◾ NO PET RENT! ◾ Online Services ◾ On-Site Maintenance ◾ On-Site Management ◾ Pet Park in Courtyard ◾ Quick Access to Wright Park with Trails ◾ Renters Insurance Program ◾ Wheelchair Access Additional Details: Deposit: $300 Terms: Variable Pets: We are very pet friendly at the Stadium and offer a fenced pet park in our courtyard, a warm and comfortable dog wash room, and we are within a minute of Wright Park where your dogs have their own park paradise! We do require a pet interview with all dogs. We do NOT charge pet rent! No monthly pet rent Just wagging tails and happy trails! Call our office at show contact info Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/thestadiumapartments# Website: www.leaseaptsnow.com?n=stadium&rp=6W62m7ycG6Na&t=wb Online Application: www.leaseaptsnow.com?n=stadium&rp=6W62m7ycG6Na&t=ap Schedule a Tour: www.leaseaptsnow.com?n=stadium&rp=6W62m7ycG6Na&t=sch All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY 47RSX0A6X69VEZ",
