ance ◾ Outdoor Covered Community Room fully equiped with entertainment and lounging ◾ Public Transportation ◾ Short Term Lease ◾ Stadium District Thriftway Grocery Store Address: 102 N G St Tacoma, WA 98403 Contact our leasing office at show contact info Mon - Fri: 9:00 AM - 6:00 PM Sat - Sun: 10:00 AM - 5:00 PM Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/thestadiumapartments# Website: www.leaseaptsnow.com?n=stadium&rp=9CnAt1qM3SoZ&t=wb Online Application: www.leaseaptsnow.com?n=stadium&rp=9CnAt1qM3SoZ&t=ap Schedule a Tour: www.leaseaptsnow.com?n=stadium&rp=9CnAt1qM3SoZ&t=sch All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY 141GEC0DEDA64G",
