        "mainpic": "256c5a25-ac76-4a89-a3a3-326a7981ebcb",
        "msg": "QR Code Link to This Post The Stadium Apartments Featured Floorplan: 1-bed with den / 1-bath / 724 sq ft Monthly Price: $2600 - $2650 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Deposit: Call Contact our leasing office at show contact info Description: The Stadium Apartments are perfect for those who enjoy spending time outside, living an active lifestyle, as well as for those who appreciate a home that's a retreat from the busyness of everyday life. Perfectly situated in one of Tacoma's most desirable neighborhoods, our homes check every item off your list. No monthly pet rent Just wagging tails and happy trails! Lease Terms: Variable Pet Policy: We are very pet friendly at the Stadium and offer a fenced pet park in our courtyard, a warm and comfortable dog wash room, and we are within a minute of Wright Park where your dogs have their own park paradise! We do require a pet interview with all dogs. We do NOT charge pet rent! Apartment Amenities: ◾ Dishwasher ◾ Disposal ◾ Efficient Appliances ◾ Electronic Thermostat ◾ Extra Storage ◾ Ice Maker ◾ Microwave ◾ Refrigerator ◾ Wheelchair Access ◾ Air Conditioner Portal for Free Standing Units ◾ Full Size Front Load Stacked Washer/Dryer ◾ Fully Furnished Units Available ◾ High Ceilings on 1st and 7th floor ◾ Large Closets and Walk-In's on Select Units ◾ Large Patio's and Balconies in Select Units. ◾ Views of Commencement Bay, Wright Park, Mt. Rainier/Cascades/Olympics, and Stadium High School Community Features: ◾ Barbecue/Grill ◾ Bicycle Storage ◾ Community Room ◾ Courtyard ◾ Electric Car Stations ◾ Elevator ◾ Fitness Center ◾ Recycling ◾ Roof Terrace ◾ Storage ◾ Community-Wide WiFi ◾ Controlled Access Building ◾ Corporate Suites ◾ Courtyard with Covered Grill ◾ Extra Storage ◾ Free Weights/Machine Weights/Squat Rack ◾ Green Building ◾ Hearing Impaired Accessible ◾ High Ceilings on 1st and 7th floor ◾ Multi Use Room ◾ On-Site Maintenance ◾ Outdoor Covered Community Room fully equiped with entertainment and lounging ◾ Public Transportation ◾ Short Term Lease ◾ Stadium District Thriftway Grocery Store Address: 102 N G St Tacoma, WA 98403 Contact our leasing office at show contact info Mon - Fri: 9:00 AM - 6:00 PM Sat - Sun: 10:00 AM - 5:00 PM Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/thestadiumapartments# Website: www.leaseaptsnow.com?n=stadium&rp=9CnAt1qM3SoZ&t=wb Online Application: www.leaseaptsnow.com?n=stadium&rp=9CnAt1qM3SoZ&t=ap Schedule a Tour: www.leaseaptsnow.com?n=stadium&rp=9CnAt1qM3SoZ&t=sch All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY 141GEC0DEDA64G",
