        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Community Location: 201 Yesler Way - Seattle, WA 98104 Monthly Price: $1785 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Apartment Details: 1 Bedroom 1 Bath | 439 sq ft Leasing Options: 12-Month Call for details: show contact info Apartment Amenities: ● Cable Ready ● Freezer ● Oven ● Smoke Free ● Tub/Shower ● Vinyl Flooring ● Air Conditioning ● Double Pane Windows ● Hardwood Floors ● High Speed Internet Access Property Features: ● 24 Hour Availability ● Controlled building access ● Disposal Chutes ● Income Restricted ● Lounge ● Maintenance on site ● Video Patrol ● Across From Light Rail Station ● City Skyline Views ● Convenient To Everything ● Fitness Center ● Key Fob Entry ● Online Services ● Public Transportation ● Renters Insurance Program ● Subway within walking distance ● Water Views Description: Availability and pricing are subject to change daily Affordable housing in the heart of Pioneer Square! We are within walking distance of Pike's Place, Lumen Field, T-Mobile Park, and The Great Wheel Seattle. The main transit line is across from our building and King Street station is a few blocks away for all of your traveling needs. There are many restaurants, cafes, and art studios located in the area as well. We are a high-rise building, conveniently located in downtown, and our building offers great amenities! Enjoy our units with charming views of Puget Sound and downtown. A 24-hour gym is located on our main floor, as well as a common area to study, read, and relax. Make Quintessa your new home by calling us today to schedule a tour! Pets: We welcome two pets per apartment home There is a $200 pet deposit per pet at move in. The monthly pet premium is $30. Please call the leasing office for our complete pet policy. $30 a month per pet 2 pet per home limit. Call for details: show contact info Website: www.leaseaptsnow.com?n=quintessa&rp=wDuRfiRBTt5c&t=wb Online Application: www.leaseaptsnow.com?n=quintessa&rp=wDuRfiRBTt5c&t=ap Schedule a Tour: www.leaseaptsnow.com?n=quintessa&rp=wDuRfiRBTt5c&t=sch 60% Income Limits: 1 - $66,00 2 - $75,420 3 - $84,840 4 - $94,260 5 - $101,820 6 - $109,380 7 - $116,940 8 - $124,440 80% Income Limits COMING IN JUNE: 1 - $88,000 2 - $100,560 3 - $113,120 4 - $125,680 5 - $135,760 6 - $145,840 7 - $155,920 8 - $165,920 All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY 3CE6ED8E9D934E",
