oring ◾ Walk-in Closets ◾ Warming Drawer ◾ Window Coverings ◾ Wood-burning Fireplace Website: www.leaseaptsnow.com?n=sterling_ridge&rp=aiYVEbzo57JC&t=wb Online Application: www.leaseaptsnow.com?n=sterling_ridge&rp=aiYVEbzo57JC&t=ap Schedule a Tour: www.leaseaptsnow.com?n=sterling_ridge&rp=aiYVEbzo57JC&t=sch Call our office at show contact info Pet-Policy: Pets Welcome Upon Approval. Limit of 2 pets per home. Pets must not exceed 25 pounds. A $250 pet fee and $250 non-refundable deposit per pet apply. There will be a $25 monthly pet rent charged per pet. Breed restrictions apply. Lease-Length: 6-Month, 7-Month, 8-Month, 9-Month, 10-Month, 11-Month, 12-Month Call for Directions Availability and pricing are subject to change daily All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY T7V6O44MXZNOJ93Z5",
