        "msg": "QR Code Link to This Post Welcome to Vue 22 Apartments Rental Information Monthly Price: $1999 - $2017 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. 1 Bedroom 1 Bath | 571 sq ft Lease Term: 12-Month, 13-Month, 14-Month, 15-Month Call us today! show contact info 4-weeks free! Apartment Amenities − Built-in desk- in select units − Built-in linen closet- in select units − Elevator access − Oversized walk-in closets- in select units − Polished quartz countertops − Private balcony or patio- in select units − Separate dining area- in select units − Smart thermostat- in select units − Wood-style plank flooring − Ceiling fans in bedrooms- in select units − Floor to ceiling double pane windows- in select units − Front-loading washer and dryer − Keyless smart lock technology − Kitchen island with pendant lighting- in select units − Mosaic tile kitchen backsplash − Stainless steel appliances including built-in microwave, refrigerator, and dishwasher − USB charging outlets in kitchen Community Features − Controlled-entry access parking garage − Co-working lounge with complimentary Wi-Fi − Dog run − Dog wash and self-service grooming area − Onsite storage available − Controlled-access bike storage and bike repair room − Easy access to WA-520, I-90, I-405, and I-5 − Live King County Metro transit screen in mail room lobby − Multi-level fitness center with yoga studio and state-of-the-art equipment − Open green space with bocce ball and oversized chess − Resident social lounge with demonstration kitchen and billiards table, shuffleboard table and arcade games − Rooftop deck featuring outdoor television, barbecue pavilion and outdoor fireplace − Virtual moving concierge - Complimentary address change, set up home services and digital moving announcements About Community Description: No matter what you're looking for, you are sure to find it at Vue 22 Apartments. Our Bellevue, WA apartments come in over 45 distinct floor plans with everything from intimate studio apartments to expansive two bedroom lofts. Each gorgeously appointed home features luxe interior flourishes, including a mosaic tile backsplash, designer pendant lighting, and USB charging outlets. Location: 2170 Bel-Red Rd Bellevue, WA 98052 show contact info Office Hours: Mon - Tue: 9:00 AM - 6:00 PM Wed: 12:00 PM - 6:00 PM Thu - Fri: 9:00 AM - 6:00 PM Sat - Sun: 10:00 AM - 5:00 PM Additional Information Call us today! show contact info Pet Policy: Dogs and cats are welcome at our community. All pet residents must have their health check, shots and be spayed or neutered upon move-in. A signed Animal Addendum is required to be on file at our leasing office. Two (2) max pets allowed. Website: www.rentalsapts.com?n=vue_22&rp=wdDqMvdfkEoA&t=wb Online Application: www.rentalsapts.com?n=vue_22&rp=wdDqMvdfkEoA&t=ap We only rent our apartments directly through our website or leasing office. We do not use any electronic funds transferring apps such as Zelle, Venmo, or Cashapp. Images are representative of the property's finishes and layout; actual unit details may vary. All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY 47B485C195804A6",
