        "info": "QR Code Link to This Post 🏡 OPEN HOUSE AT THE RETREAT AT BOTHELL! 🏡 Looking for a new place to call home? Come experience resort-style living at The Retreat at Bothell and see why so many residents love calling our community home. ✨ Tour our beautifully updated 1, 2, and 3-bedroom apartment homes ✨ Explore our resort-style amenities ✨ Enjoy complimentary refreshments ✨ Meet our friendly leasing team ✨ Take a private tour of the community 📅 Open House Dates Sunday, June 14 | 1:00 PM – 3:00 PM Sunday, June 21 | 1:00 PM – 3:00 PM Sunday, June 28 | 1:00 PM – 3:00 PM 🎉 ENTER TO WIN A 55\" ROKU TV! 🎉 Just for attending, you'll receive 1 raffle ticket for our TV giveaway. Want even more chances to win? 🏠 Apply and lease a home during the Open House and receive: ✅ 10 additional raffle tickets ✅ $500 OFF move-in costs ✅ A chance to make The Retreat at Bothell your new home 📺 The winner of the 55\" Roku TV will be drawn on Wednesday, July 1st. Whether you're actively apartment hunting or just exploring your options, we'd love to meet you and show you around. The Retreat at Bothell 18101 126th Ave NE Bothell, WA 98011 📞 show contact info Come see what makes The Retreat at Bothell more than just an apartment community—it's a place to relax, recharge, and feel at home. We can't wait to welcome you! 🏡✨ Restrictions may apply. See leasing office for complete raffle and move-in incentive details.",
