strictions apply. Limit of 2 pets per home. Non-refundable pet fee is $400 per pet. Monthly pet rent of $25 will be charged per pet. All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY GDKT8SN0TCO7C7VB",
