        "msg": "QR Code Link to This Post Come home to a great community - Copper Gate! Address: 4798 Auburn Way North Auburn, WA 98002 Call Today! show contact info Beds: 2 / Baths: 2 / Size: 982 sq ft Monthly Price: $2138 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Relaxation and recreation are at the forefront, with an indoor fitness center, outdoor pool, splash pad, and a cyber café available to all residents. We are pet-friendly, too, so your four-legged friends can roam around the neighborhood. As a resident of Copper Gate in Auburn, WA, stunning landscapes, thoughtful amenities, and extraordinary services will make each day a delight. Deposit: $400 Length of Lease: 6-Month Property Features: ✓ Basketball Court ✓ Business Center ✓ Community Garden Nursery ✓ Cyber Cafe ✓ Horseshoes ✓ Indoor Gymnasium ✓ Indoor Playground ✓ On-site Bike Repair ✓ Outdoor Barbecues ✓ Pet Friendly ✓ 16 Buildings and 1 Clubhouse ✓ 4 Outdoor Playgrounds ✓ Easy Access to Nearby Farmers Market ✓ Game Room with Pool Tables ✓ Garages and Carports Available ✓ Indoor State-of-the-art Fitness Center ✓ Nearby Walking Trails ✓ Outdoor Sports Court ✓ Picnic Shelter with Tables ✓ Shimmering Swimming Pool and Splash Pad Apartment Amenities: ✓ Balcony and Patio ✓ Black Appliances ✓ Ceiling Fans ✓ Energy-efficient Construction ✓ Full-size Washer and Dryer in Home ✓ Fully-equipped Kitchen ✓ Large Closets ✓ Microwave ✓ Patio ✓ Spacious Bedrooms ✓ Business Center ✓ Clubhouse ✓ Fitness Center ✓ Garage ✓ Playground ✓ Pool Pets: Pets Welcome Upon Approval. Breed restrictions apply. Limit of 2 pets per home. Non-refundable pet fee is $400 per pet. Monthly pet rent of $25 will be charged per pet. Business Hours: Mon - Fri: 9:00 AM - 6:00 PM Ready to Lease? Call Today! show contact info Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/coppergateapartments Website: www.apt-rental.com?n=copper_gate&rp=sCpsyeRVtHoY&t=wb Online Application: www.apt-rental.com?n=copper_gate&rp=sCpsyeRVtHoY&t=ap Schedule a Tour: www.apt-rental.com?n=copper_gate&rp=sCpsyeRVtHoY&t=sch All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY 0EJTVKAC97H2ARM",
