        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Welcome home to Redmond Park! Our Bellevue apartments and town homes – adjacent to Goldsmith Park and directly across the street from the Microsoft campus – are surrounded by lush landscaping and soaring trees, feeling as if you are in the secluded country. But with businesses, great shopping and dining close by in downtown Redmond and at Redmond Town Center, you never feel far from anything. Each apartment home provides spacious floor plans, modern kitchens, designer touches, and plenty of storage. Enjoy fabulous amenities as well, including outdoor pools, fitness centers and business lounge. This apartment features: 1100 SQFT* VIRTUAL TOUR AVAILABLE! on our website Two-story townhouse Open concept design, see your living room from your kitchen! Fully-equipped kitchen with refrigerator, stove, microwave, dishwasher, sink, plenty of storage, and a window letting in natural light! Get cozy… wood-burning fireplace for during the colder months Convenient washer and dryer on the 1st floor Ample closets with organizing shelves in the 2nd floor hallway Light & bright double master bedrooms each with its own bath, generous closet, large windows Spacious partially fenced-in back patio Luxury wood-style flooring throughout Pet-friendly home Tons of storage Free or Reserved Parking Available Professional On-site Management Photos in ad may not be of actual apartment, however we try our best to use photos similar to the floor plan. Come Visit us! Redmond Park Apartments 14700 NE 35th St Bellevue, WA 98007 https://livecreativejuices.com/xwzk7sy6/redmond-park-apartments Contact us today to schedule a tour! Call show contact info Office Hours Tuesday - Friday 10:00 am - 6:00 pm Saturday 10:00 am - 4:00 pm Closed Sunday & Monday Photos in ad may not be of actual apartment, however we try our best to use photos similar to the floor plan.",
