        "msg": "QR Code Link to This Post You Read it Right!! Only 500/wk - All Inclusive! Attractive New Lower Weekly or Monthly Rates (include another bed for only 100 more) Includes: Wi-Fi, Free Cable TV, Pool, 24-Hour Concierge, Room, Individually Controlled AC/Heat, Kids Are FREE Motel 6 - Seattle South show contact info 20651 Military Road South Seattle WA 98198 Located just two miles from SeaTac International Airport, Motel 6 - Seattle South offers a convenient and comfortable stay for travelers exploring the Pacific Northwest. The community's prime location places guests within easy reach of major highways, public transportation, and a variety of shopping and dining options. Guests can enjoy modern rooms equipped with free Wi-Fi, making it simple to stay connected during their visit. The area around SeaTac features numerous parks such as Angle Lake Park and North SeaTac Park, providing ample opportunities for outdoor recreation. APARTMENT AND COMMUNITY AMENITIES - Accessible Rooms Plus - Closed-captioned TV Accessibility - Free Parking, 24 hours - Ice/Vending Machines - Kids Stay Free - Airport within 20 miles - Truck Parking - Shower/tub Combination - Free WiFi (Wi-Fi) - Restaurant Nearby - Free Coffee - Vending Machines Visitors can also explore local attractions like the iconic Space Needle, which offers breathtaking views of Seattle's skyline and the surrounding mountains. SeaTac hosts vibrant community events, including the International Festival and Shakespeare in the Park, fostering a lively local atmosphere. For families, Motel 6 provides family-friendly amenities, and kids stay free when accompanied by a parent, making it a great choice for group trips. Whether you're in town for business, leisure, or family fun, Motel 6 - Seattle South delivers great value, comfort, and a strategic location to maximize your travel experience.",
