        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Only 500/wk if you call now! Includes: Wi-Fi, AC/Heat, Pool, Your Luxury Room, 24-Hour Desk, Kids Stay FREE, Cable Television Experience comfortable and affordable accommodations just minutes from Seattle-Tacoma International Airport at Motel 6 Seattle South. Conveniently situated off I-5 at Military Road, this location provides easy access to major highways, shopping, dining, and public transportation options. Guests can enjoy modern rooms equipped with free Wi-Fi, ensuring connectivity during their stay. The community offers nearby outdoor attractions such as Angle Lake Park, Valley Ridge Park, and North SeaTac Park, perfect for outdoor recreation and relaxation. Onsite & In-Unit Features > Restaurant Nearby > Pets Allowed > Wheelchair Accessible Parking, Concierge & Registration > Private Bathroom > Mass Transit > Free Coffee > Shower/tub Combination > Vending Machines > Free WiFi (Wi-Fi) > Free Parking, 24 hours > Recently Renovated (Select Rooms) > Free Local Calls show contact info Motel 6 - Seattle South Cultural events like the International Festival and Parade, Shakespeare in the Park, and the Music in the Park Series enrich the local scene, providing opportunities to engage with the vibrant community. A short drive takes visitors to the iconic Space Needle, where sweeping views of the Seattle skyline await. The tranquil Highline SeaTac Botanical Gardens and various parks offer peaceful escapes from urban life. Whether visiting for business or leisure, Motel 6 Seattle South combines affordability, comfort, and convenience for a memorable stay in the Pacific Northwest.",
