        "info": "QR Code Link to This Post Signature Pointe Apartments lies alongside the Green River in Kent and is surrounded by tall evergreen trees. The community offers many amenities for residents to enjoy year-round, from outdoor tennis courts, playgrounds, and fire pits, to indoor fitness centers and pools. You'll always find something to keep you busy here at Signature Pointe. Apartment Features: Full-Size Washer/Dryer Double Sinks Built-In Bookshelves Over-sized Walk-In Closets Microwave Top Floor Units Feature 19-ft Ceilings Community Features: Fully Equipped Fitness Center Bordered by the Interurban Trail Heated Indoor Pool, Sauna, & Spa Close to Schools, Restaurants, & Shops Outdoor BBQs & Firepits Translation Service Available Call: CL Tracking # 25102 62nd Ave S, Kent, WA 98032 Our resort-style community embodies all the elements necessary for great apartment living. From our unique architecture and spacious floor plans, to our state-of-the-art recreation pavilion, you will love calling Signature Pointe your new home! Call now and schedule a tour appointment! Pet Policy: Cats & Dogs Allowed Limit 2 Pets Per Home 1 Pet: $20 Pet Rent per month 1 Pet: $250 Pet Deposit (Refundable) 1 Pet: $250Pet Fee (Non-Refundable) Additional Pets Fee: $250/ Pet (Non-Refundable) Breed Restrictions May Apply Minimum Age Limit May Apply Office Hours: Monday: 9am - 6pm Tuesday: 9am - 6pm Wednesday: 9am - 6pm Thursday: 9am - 6pm Friday: 9am - 6pm Saturday: 9am -5pm Sunday: CLOSED",
