        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post 1707 Merrill Creek Pkwy, Everett, WA 98203 Bedrooms:  2 Bathrooms:  2 Square Feet:  968 Rent Price:  1964 Welcome home to beautiful Greens of Merrill Creek Apartment Homes in Everett, Washington. Let us help you enjoy more than 1600 acres of beautiful public parks, trails, and playgrounds and nearly 50 miles of freshwater and saltwater shoreline. Everett is home to some of the best salmon and steelhead fishing in the world, boasting the largest public marina on the West Coast. At Greens of Merrill Creek we offer our residents one, two, or three bedroom floor plans. Each apartment home includes a built in computer desk, a private patio or balcony, a full pantry, a gourmet all electric kitchen, plush wall to wall carpeting, spacious walk in closets, mini and vertical blinds and a full size washer and dryer. Let us welcome you home. Amenities Include: Dishwasher High Ceilings Cable Ready Playground Extra Storage Window Coverings Efficient Appliances Wheelchair Access One Assigned Parking Space Refrigerator Public Transportation Nearby Washer/Dryer Call: show contact info For more information, visit us at: https://cirrusmgmt.com/pxxzf36a/greens-of-merrill-creek pricing and availability is subject to change daily.",
