        "info": "QR Code Link to This Post Welcome to Woodhaven! 4632 Fowler Ave Everett, WA 98203 Call for details: show contact info Rental Size: 2 BR - 1 BA - 850 sq ft Monthly Price: $1800 - $2018 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Lease Length: 6-Month, 8-Month, 9-Month, 10-Month, 12-Month From designer updates like faux wood flooring, quartz countertops, shaker-style cabinets, and conveniences like on-site storage and laundry facilities, explore our homes and see the joys of home at Woodhaven. A robust setting and friendly staff welcome you - we love your furry friends too! Enjoy the large pet park, community garden, playground, and much more. Our community features: ◾ 24 Hour Maintenance ◾ BBQ/Picnic Area ◾ Beautiful Landscaping ◾ Community Garden ◾ Cornhole ◾ Courtyard ◾ Laundry Facilities ◾ Off Street Parking ◾ Online Services ◾ Community Garden ◾ Easy Access to Historic Downtown Everett ◾ Minutes from Everett Naval Station ◾ Pet Play Area ◾ Playground ◾ Recycling ◾ Renters Insurance Program ◾ Secluded Forest Park Location ◾ Shuffleboard ◾ Storage Units for Rent Our apartment features: ◾ Carpeting ◾ Ceiling Fans ◾ Heating ◾ Linen Closet ◾ Oven ◾ Patio/Balcony in Most Units ◾ Range ◾ Refrigerator ◾ Smoke Free ◾ Tub/Shower ◾ Beautiful Views from Balconies in Select Units ◾ Built-in Bookshelves ◾ Cable Ready ◾ Dishwasher ◾ Double Pane Windows ◾ Faux Wood Flooring ◾ Granite Countertops ◾ Upgraded Interiors ◾ Vinyl Flooring ◾ Window Covering Call for details: -- show contact info -- Our Pet-Policy: 2 pets per apartment home $50 pet rent per pet $400 deposit per pet $200 non-refundable deposit for 1st pet, $250 for additional pet The following breed restrictions apply - Akita, Alaskan Malamute, Chow, Dalmatian, Doberman Pinscher, German Shepherd, Great Dane, Husky, Rottweiler, Saint Bernard, Wolf Dog Hybrids and all Pit Bull breeds. Website: www.apt-rental.com?n=woodhaven&rp=jG4cm8MUy9Cf&t=wb Online Application: www.apt-rental.com?n=woodhaven&rp=jG4cm8MUy9Cf&t=ap 3D Virtual Tour: www.apt-rental.com?n=woodhaven&rp=jG4cm8MUy9Cf&t=trt Schedule a Tour: www.apt-rental.com?n=woodhaven&rp=jG4cm8MUy9Cf&t=sch All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY 6866967C5B3149B",
