        "info": "QR Code Link to This Post 6248 S 242nd Pl, Kent, WA 98032 Welcome Home to ReNew on James Welcome to the ReNew on James, Kent's premier luxury apartment community featuring spacious one, two, three-bedroom apartment homes for rent, exquisitely designed with your interest in mind. Indulge in renovated interiors including:Upgraded Carpeting, Modernized Cabinetry, In-House Washer & Dryer, Vaulted Ceilings, Oversized Closets When you're ready to head outside, enhance your active lifestyle with a sauna spa sundeck, heated pool, and an expanded fitness center. Less than a few miles from Kent, ReNew on James is conveniently located near Green River, Riverfront Park, and Russell Rd Park, near some of the best entertainment that the city of Kent has to offer. Enjoy easy access to the Interstate 167, bringing you to the area's best shopping, dining, and entertainment. Contact us today! Apartment Features: Quartz Countertop Matte Black and Brushed Nickel Fixtures Available Plush Modern Carpet Easy to Clean LVP Flooring Crisp White Paint Package Community Features: Bark Park Covered Assigned Parking Amazon Package Lockers Garages Avaliable Valet Trash Service Call: show contact info For more information, visit us at: https://trinity-apt.com/uaf3fery/renew-on-james Pricing and availability are subject to change.",
