        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post 1206 NW Tahoe Ln, Silverdale, WA 98383 WELCOME TO Cascade RidgeImagine waking up in a spacious, beautifully designed apartment nestled in the heart of Silverdale, Washington. At Cascade Ridge, we don’t just offer a place to live—we offer a lifestyle and a community you look forward to coming home to. Whether you’re looking for a cozy one-bedroom retreat, a two-bedroom haven, or a three-bedroom space to grow, you’ll find everything you need to feel right at home. From modern finishes to thoughtful features, your new home is designed to make life more enjoyable. And the best part? You’ll have access to incredible amenities, like a club-style fitness center with a rock-climbing wall, a seasonal heated pool, and even an off-leash dog park for your furry friends. Apartment Features: In-Home Washer & Dryer Open-Concept Design Spacious Floor Plans Oversized Closets & Additional Storage Private Patio or Balcony Cable Ready Community Features: 24-Hour Package Lockers Seasonally Heated Outdoor Pool Golf Simulator Club-Style Fitness Center Professionally Managed Call: show contact info For more information, visit us at: https://gre-apartments.com/diidbqkj/cascade-ridge Please leave your name and contact number when replying to this posting. *Pricing and availability are subject to change daily. Photos may not be of the exact advertised unit. Please contact us today for the most up to date information!",
