        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post 2 Bedroom 1.5 Bathroom | 890 sq ft Monthly Price: $1750 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Hillview Apartments 12833 60th Lane South G-02 G-02 Seattle, WA 98178 Call us today! show contact info Description: FREE RENT!! Now Available!! 2 Bed/1.5 Bath with IN UNIT LAUNDRY 12833 60th Lane South G-02, G-02, Seattle, WA 98178 2 bd, 1.5 ba | Available 8/10/26 Looking for more than just an apartment_ Discover why Hillview Apartments was recently nominated by The Seattle Times for Best Apartment Community in the Pacific Northwest. Our thoughtfully designed one-bedroom homes offer approximately 890 square feet of comfortable living space, with the features that make everyday life easier and more enjoyable. Each home includes: • Full-size washer and dryer in every apartment • Private balcony with additional storage space • Cozy wood-burning fireplace • Reserved parking • Pet-friendly community with an on-site dog area Nestled among mature evergreens between Seattle and Renton, Hillview offers the convenience of city access with the comfort of a neighborhood feel. Located directly on the King County Metro route, commuting to downtown Seattle, Renton, Tukwila, or SeaTac is simple and convenient. At Hillview, we're continually investing in our community through ongoing improvements and resident-focused enhancements. Combined with seasonal events and a welcoming atmosphere, it's easy to see why our residents are proud to call Hillview home. Diversity • Connection • Community Come experience the difference of an award-nominated community and find your place at Hillview Apartments. Schedule your tour today! Lease Details: $1680 Rent $170 Water/Sewage/Garbage $200 Admin/Hold Fee $600 Refundable Deposit $66 Application Fee - Here is the link to apply: www.apts-rental.com?n=hillview&rp=cUpGRTmZiiTS&t=sch - Cosigner Link: https://apply.alliance2020.com/#/view/wj8m *Please note when applying to select all other cities as we are unincorporated King County and not City of Seattle Virtual tour - https://www. /view-3d-home/b20e6dba-b4ce-4e9b-96ed-af1c8e849e8d_setAttribution=mls&wl=true&utm_source=dashboard We do not accept comprehensive reusable tenant screening reports as defined by and pursuant to RCW 59.18. Icon Real Estate Services is an equal opportunity housing provider who commits to complying with all federal, state, and local fair housing laws. We will not discriminate against any person based on race, color, religion, national origin, sex (including gender identity and sexual orientation), familial status, disability, or any other protected classes specified by applicable laws. All applicants are scored on the same standards; one person, group, or family at a time on a first-come, first-served basis. All vacancies will be filled by the first qualified applicant who can move in closest to the availability date Amenities Dishwasher Balcony w/Storage Nightly Security Patrol New mail/parcel boxes Community Courtyard Assigned Parking Landscaping Services On-Site Maintenance On-Site Property Manager Dog Park In Unit Laundry King County Bus Line Easy Access to I-5 CCTV Pet Friendly Up to 50 lbs Rental Terms Rent: $1,750 Application Fee: $66 Security Deposit: $800 Available 8/10/26 Pet Policy Cats allowed Small dogs allowed Utilities Water Sewer Garbage Recycling Appliances Refrigerator Dishwasher Garbage Disposal Stove/Oven Washer and Dryer Apartment Amenities: Our Residents Enjoy: Additional Details: Deposit: Call Terms: 12-Month Pets: Max 2 per unit. Call us today! show contact info Website: www.apts-rental.com?n=hillview&rp=cUpGRTmZiiTS&t=wb Online Application: www.apts-rental.com?n=hillview&rp=cUpGRTmZiiTS&t=ap Schedule a Tour: {URL_SCHD} All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY 36J4VS75N2ZSZTB",
