        "info": "QR Code Link to This Post 1 Bedroom 1 Bathroom | 699 sq ft Monthly Price: $1950 - $2099 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Sunset Terrace 2715 Sunset Ln NE Renton, WA 98056 Call us for more information! show contact info Description: Sunset Terrace is located at 2715 Sunset Ln NE Renton, WA. Sunset Terrace offers Studio to 2-bedroom apartments ranging in size from 456 to 1206 sq.ft. This apartment community is pet friendly, welcoming both cats and dogs. Discover Your Perfect Home: Schedule an Appointment for a Tour Today! Apartment Amenities: − Dishwasher − Disposal − High Speed Internet Access − Microwave − Quartz Countertops − Smoke Free − Stainless Steel Appliances − Vinyl Flooring − Walk In Closets − Walk-In Closets − Air conditioning ports for portable unit − Choose from light or dark interior scheme − Convenient in-unit washer and dryer − Juliette balconies/Private patios − Kitchen islands with pendant lighting − Pantry closets − Quartz countertops and satin nickel hardware − Under cabinet lighting − Wired for easy cable-ready connection Our Residents Enjoy: − Business Center − Clubhouse − EV Charging − Fitness Center − Key Fob Entry − Lounge − Multi Use Room − On-Site Retail − Package Service − Recycling − Cycling hub with substantial bike parking − Dual elevators for up and down ease − EV car chargers − Park and mountain views − Parking garage − Professional on-site management and maintenance − Secure entry with video access calling − Secure package lockers − Trash chute and eco-conscious recycling room − Welcoming lobby with fireplace and soft seating Additional Details: Deposit: Call Terms: 6-Month, 7-Month, 8-Month, 9-Month, 10-Month, 11-Month, 12-Month Pets: Please see Pets page for more details! Call us for more information! show contact info Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/LiveSunsetTerrace/ Website: www.rentalsapts.com?n=sunset_terrace&rp=4fpoBsaqgCXj&t=wb Online Application: www.rentalsapts.com?n=sunset_terrace&rp=4fpoBsaqgCXj&t=ap Schedule a Tour: www.rentalsapts.com?n=sunset_terrace&rp=4fpoBsaqgCXj&t=sch All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY BHVORL4IHIC03A0",
