        "info": "QR Code Link to This Post Welcome to Copper Gate! 4798 Auburn Way North Auburn, WA 98002 Call us for more information! show contact info Rental Size: 1 BR - 1 BA - 714 sq ft Please call Lease Length: 6-Month Offering a selection of one, two, three, and four-bedroom apartments for rent, Copper Gate gives residents an enjoyable experience in the best community in the area. Inside your spacious home, you can easily unwind with the latest features. Fully equipped kitchens, a full-sized washer and dryer, and a balcony or patio are all a given. Having a variety of amenities is how we aim to provide the best in apartment living. Our community features: ● Basketball Court ● Business Center ● Community Garden Nursery ● Cyber Cafe ● Horseshoes ● Indoor Gymnasium ● Indoor Playground ● On-site Bike Repair ● Outdoor Barbecues ● Pet Friendly ● 16 Buildings and 1 Clubhouse ● 4 Outdoor Playgrounds ● Courtesy Patrol ● Easy Access to Nearby Farmers Market ● Game Room with Pool Tables ● Garages and Carports Available ● Indoor State-of-the-art Fitness Center ● Outdoor Sports Court ● Picnic Shelter with Tables ● Shimmering Swimming Pool and Splash Pad Our apartment features: ● Balcony and Patio ● Black Appliances ● Carpeted Floors in Bedrooms ● Ceiling Fans ● Energy-efficient Construction ● Full-size Washer and Dryer in Home ● Fully-equipped Kitchen ● Microwave ● Patio ● Spacious Bedrooms ● Business Center ● Clubhouse ● Fitness Center ● Garage ● Playground ● Pool Call us for more information! -- show contact info -- Our Pet-Policy: Pets Welcome Upon Approval. Breed restrictions apply. Limit of 2 pets per home. Non-refundable pet fee is $400 per pet. Monthly pet rent of $25 will be charged per pet. Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/coppergateapartments Website: www.apt-rental.com?n=copper_gate&rp=o85D6asphUFz&t=wb Online Application: www.apt-rental.com?n=copper_gate&rp=o85D6asphUFz&t=ap Schedule a Tour: www.apt-rental.com?n=copper_gate&rp=o85D6asphUFz&t=sch All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY GDKT8SN0TCO7C7VB",
