        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post -- Copper Gate -- Phone Number: show contact info Monthly Price: $1786 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Apartment: 1 Bedroom | 1 Bathroom Square Footage: 819 sq ft Relaxation and recreation are at the forefront, with an indoor fitness center, outdoor pool, splash pad, and a cyber café available to all residents. We are pet-friendly, too, so your four-legged friends can roam around the neighborhood. As a resident of Copper Gate in Auburn, WA, stunning landscapes, thoughtful amenities, and extraordinary services will make each day a delight. Pet Policy: Pets Welcome Upon Approval. Breed restrictions apply. Limit of 2 pets per home. Non-refundable pet fee is $400 per pet. Monthly pet rent of $25 will be charged per pet. Check out our beautiful community featuring: ● Basketball Court ● Business Center ● Community Garden Nursery ● Cyber Cafe ● Horseshoes ● Indoor Gymnasium ● Indoor Playground ● On-site Bike Repair ● Outdoor Barbecues ● Pet Friendly ● 16 Buildings and 1 Clubhouse ● 4 Outdoor Playgrounds ● Courtesy Patrol ● Easy Access to Nearby Farmers Market ● Garages and Carports Available ● Indoor State-of-the-art Fitness Center ● Nearby Walking Trails ● Outdoor Sports Court ● Picnic Shelter with Tables ● Shimmering Swimming Pool and Splash Pad Apartment features include: ● Balcony and Patio ● Black Appliances ● Carpeted Floors in Bedrooms ● Ceiling Fans ● Full-size Washer and Dryer in Home ● Fully-equipped Kitchen ● Large Closets ● Microwave ● Patio ● Spacious Bedrooms ● Business Center ● Clubhouse ● Fitness Center ● Garage ● Playground ● Pool Phone Number: show contact info Mon - Fri: 9:00 AM - 6:00 PM Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/coppergateapartments Website: www.lease-apts.com?n=copper_gate&rp=igrGt9FTRyNR&t=wb Online Application: www.lease-apts.com?n=copper_gate&rp=igrGt9FTRyNR&t=ap Schedule a Tour: www.lease-apts.com?n=copper_gate&rp