        "msg": "QR Code Link to This Post Welcome to The Stadium Apartments Rental Information Monthly Price: $2000 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Studio Bedroom 1 Bath | 546 sq ft Lease Term: Variable Phone: show contact info No monthly pet rent Just wagging tails and happy trails! Apartment Amenities ❖ Dishwasher ❖ Disposal ❖ Efficient Appliances ❖ Electronic Thermostat ❖ Extra Storage ❖ Ice Maker ❖ Microwave ❖ Refrigerator ❖ Wheelchair Access ❖ Air Conditioner Portal for Free Standing Units ❖ Full Size Front Load Stacked Washer/Dryer ❖ Fully Furnished Units Available ❖ High Ceilings on 1st and 7th floor ❖ Large Closets and Walk-In's on Select Units ❖ Large Patio's and Balconies in Select Units. ❖ Views of Commencement Bay, Wright Park, Mt. Rainier/Cascades/Olympics, and Stadium High School Community Features ❖ Barbecue/Grill ❖ Community Room ❖ Courtyard ❖ Dog Park ❖ Electric Car Stations ❖ Elevator ❖ Fitness Center ❖ Lounge ❖ Recycling ❖ Storage ❖ 24 Hour Access ❖ Controlled Access Building ❖ Controlled Access Parking Garage ❖ Courtyard with Covered Grill ❖ Disposal Chutes ❖ Floor to Ceiling Windows on Select Units ❖ Fully Furnished Units Available ❖ Green Building ❖ Light Rail Stop ❖ NO PET RENT! ❖ On-Site Maintenance ❖ Package Service ❖ Public Transportation ❖ Quick Access to Wright Park with Trails ❖ Vision Impaired Accessible About Community Description: The Stadium Apartments are in the heart of Tacoma's Stadium District offering Studio, One, and Two Bedroom homes! Stunning views of Puget Sound, Mount Rainier and the Olympics will be available right from the comfort of your new home. Location: 102 N G St Tacoma, WA 98403 show contact info Office Hours: Mon - Fri: 9:00 AM - 6:00 PM Sat - Sun: 10:00 AM - 5:00 PM Additional Information Phone: show contact info Pet Policy: We are very pet friendly at the Stadium and offer a fenced pet park in our courtyard, a warm and comfortable dog wash room, and we are within a minute of Wright Park where your dogs have their own park paradise! We do require a pet interview with all dogs. We do NOT charge pet rent! Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/thestadiumapartments# Website: www.lease-apts.com?n=stadium&rp=f3TDeYRtx68K&t=wb Online Application: www.lease-apts.com?n=stadium&rp=f3TDeYRtx68K&t=ap Schedule a Tour: www.lease-apts.com?n=stadium&rp=f3TDeYRtx68K&t=sch All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY 47RSX0A6X69VEZ",
