        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Sunrise Lane Apartment Homes Featured Floorplan: 1-bed / 1-bath / 741 sq ft Monthly Price: $1795 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Deposit: $400 Call us today! show contact info Description: Tucked away in the Westmont neighborhood, our gated community offers a peaceful retreat with easy access to everything you need. Choose from our spacious 1, 2, and 3-bedroom apartments, designed with open layouts, extra closet space, and classic finishes that make you feel right at home. $1000 Off Move-In Costs - Limited Time Special! Join us at Sunrise Lane! *Available on select homes for a limited time. Lease Terms: 6-Month, 7-Month, 8-Month, 9-Month, 10-Month, 11-Month, 12-Month Pet Policy: Monthly Pet Rent: $50 per pet Deposit: $400 refundable deposit (for up to 2 pets) One-Time Fee: $200 non-refundable pet fee for 1st pet, $100 fee for 2nd pet Number of Pets: 2 pets per apartment home Weight Limit: No weight limit restrictions Age Restrictions: Dogs must be at least 6 months old Breed Restrictions: The following breed restrictions apply - Akita, Alaskan Malamute, Chow, Dalmatian, Doberman Pinscher, German Shepherd, Great Dane, Husky, Pit Bull Terriers*, Rottweiler, Saint Bernard, Wolf Dog Hybrids and all Pit Bull breeds (American Pit Bull Terriers, American Apartment Amenities: ◾ Dining Room ◾ Dishwasher ◾ Fireplace ◾ Linen Closet ◾ Pantry ◾ Patio/Balcony ◾ Smoke Free ◾ Walk-In Closets ◾ Washer/Dryer ◾ Baseboard Heat ◾ Energy Efficient Appliances ◾ Views Community Features: ◾ Business Center ◾ Controlled Access/Gated ◾ Courtyard ◾ Fitness Center ◾ Garage ◾ More info on Garage ◾ Playground ◾ Pool ◾ Recycling ◾ Spa/Hot Tub ◾ Availability 24 Hours ◾ BBQ/Grill Area ◾ Cabana/Gazebo ◾ Cardio Machines ◾ On-Site Maintenance ◾ On-Site Management ◾ Picnic Area ◾ Resident Lounge ◾ Trash Pickup - Curbside ◾ Weight Machines Address: 12522 8th Ave W Everett, WA 98204 Call us today! show contact info Mon - Fri: 9:00 AM - 6:00 PM Website: www.apts-rental.com?n=sunrise_lane&rp=6FSFqJgVHo5x&t=wb Online Application: www.apts-rental.com?n=sunrise_lane&rp=6FSFqJgVHo5x&t=ap Schedule a Tour: www.apts-rental.com?n=sunrise_lane&rp=6FSFqJgVHo5x&t=sch All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY ML7XDO8Z77ZKZEN",
