        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Village on Main Apartments Visit our community today! 5020 Main St Ruston, WA 98407 Contact our leasing office at show contact info $1,500 off when you lease select homes by 6/15/26!* *RESTRICTIONS APPLY. CONTACT US FOR DETAILS. Monthly Price: $2441 - $2498 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Apartment Type: 1-BR 1-BA Apartment Size: 792 sq ft Lease Terms: 3-Month, 4-Month, 5-Month, 6-Month, 7-Month, 8-Month, 9-Month, 10-Month, 11-Month, 12-Month, 13-Month Pet Policy: Dogs and cats are welcome at our community. All pet residents must have their health check, shots and be spayed or neutered upon move-in. A signed Animal Addendum is required to be on file at our leasing office. Two (2) max pets allowed and breed restriction! What you'll find in our community: ● Along the Point Ruston Waterwalk ● Bike storage ● Controlled-entry access ● Landscaped courtyard with outdoor seating ● Pet friendly ● State-of-the-art fitness center ● 50 onsite retail with unique eateries and shopping right at your doorstep ● Package locker with 24/7 access to packages ● Private parking garage with direct access elevators ● Resident social lounge with demonstration kitchen and pool table ● Virtual Moving Concierge: Complimentary address change, set up home services and digital moving announcements ● Worry-free 24-hour onsite maintenance Description: Select your dream home from a diverse collection of thoughtfully designed luxury homes available with us, which includes variety of arrangements for each home with access to world-class amenities and is finished to reflect your unique personal taste. This apartment comes with: ● 9-foot ceilings ● Elevator access ● Furnished apartments available ● In-home washer and dryer ● Oversized walk-in closets ● Private balcony or patio ● Separate dining area ● Wood-style plank flooring ● Air conditioning with programmable remote thermostat ● Breakfast bar with pendant lighting ● Expansive bay windows with 2-inch wood blinds ● Income Qualified Apartment Home (MFTE) ● Panoramic views of South Puget Sound, the Olympic Mountains, and Mount Rainier ● Polished kitchen countertops ● Stainless steel appliances including built-in microwave, refrigerator, and dishwasher Contact our leasing office at show contact info Mon - Tue: 9:00 AM - 6:00 PM Wed: 12:00 PM - 6:00 PM Thu - Fri: 9:00 AM - 6:00 PM Sat: 10:00 AM - 5:00 PM Appointment scheduled preferred Visit our website to schedule a personal tour! Website: www.apt-rental.com?n=village_on_main&rp=x1No2z6XSWUK&t=wb Online Application: www.apt-rental.com?n=village_on_main&rp=x1No2z6XSWUK&t=ap We only rent our apartments directly through our website or leasing office. We do not use any electronic funds transferring apps such as Zelle, Venmo, or Cashapp. All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY 37TS4109EA8D1SSG",
