        "info": "QR Code Link to This Post Urban Center Apartments Located at: 15907 Ash Way Lynnwood, WA 98087 Featured apartment home: 1 bed | 1 bath | 655 sq ft Please call Contact Info: show contact info Welcome to Urban Center apartments, a vibrant community where comfort meets sophistication in the heart of Lynnwood, WA. Situated near Interstate 5 and 164th Street SW, you will have easy access to some of the area's best shopping, dining, and entertainment. Explore nearby malls, theatres, and parks-all just minutes away. Whether you're looking to relax at home or take advantage of all that the community has to offer, you'll find everything you need here. Apply by 8/24 to receive this special offer. Wonderful Amenities! ◾ Business Center with Printer ◾ Clubhouse with Kitchen and Free Wifi ◾ Conference and Meeting Room ◾ Controlled Access Entry ◾ Elevators ◾ Pet Waste Stations ◾ Pet-friendly ◾ Private Outdoor Space ◾ Underground Parking ◾ Additional Storage Available ◾ Bark Park ◾ Billiards Parlor ◾ Gated Access ◾ Nearby Shopping and Restaurants ◾ Outdoor Lounge with Barbecue ◾ State-of-the-art Fitness Center ◾ Theater Room Apartment Features! ◾ Balcony ◾ Built-in Microwave ◾ Cable Ready ◾ Carpet ◾ Heating ◾ Linen Closet ◾ Microwave ◾ Sprinkler System ◾ Wheelchair Accessible (Rooms) ◾ Window Coverings ◾ Dishwasher ◾ High Speed Internet Access ◾ Island Kitchen ◾ Large Bedrooms ◾ Storage Space ◾ Stunning New Black Appliances ◾ Views ◾ Vinyl Flooring ◾ Walk-In Closets ◾ Washer and Dryer in Home Summer Spectacular Special - 6 weeks FREE on select homes. Don't wait ~ Schedule your tour today! Hours: Mon - Fri: 9:00 AM - 5:00 PM Sat: 10:00 AM - 5:00 PM Sun: 11:00 AM - 5:00 PM Contact Info: show contact info Website: www.rentalsapts.com?n=urban_center&rp=gdHYqXUb28ya&t=wb Online Application: www.rentalsapts.com?n=urban_center&rp=gdHYqXUb28ya&t=ap Schedule a Tour: www.rentalsapts.com?n=urban_center&rp=gdHYqXUb28ya&t=sch Terms: 12-Month Pet Policy: Pets Welcome Upon Appro