        "msg": "QR Code Link to This Post Urban Center Apartments Please call SIZE: 671 - 731 sq ft BEDROOMS: 1 BATHROOMS: 1 LEASE TERMS: 12-Month Call us today! show contact info Summer Spectacular Special - 6 weeks FREE on select homes. Don't wait ~ Schedule your tour today! APARTMENT HOME FEATURES: − Balcony − Built-in Microwave − Cable Ready − Carpet − Double Pane Windows − Heating − Linen Closet − Microwave − Pantry − Window Coverings − Dishwasher − High Speed Internet Access − Island Kitchen − Large Bedrooms − Storage Space − Stunning New Black Appliances − Views − Vinyl Flooring − Walk-In Closets − Washer and Dryer in Home Have you heard that Urban Center apartments in Lynnwood, Washington is under new management? With a selection of one, two, and three-bedroom apartments for rent, our residents enjoy a truly exceptional living experience. Inside each home, modern features are designed for ease and comfort, including in-unit washers and dryers, dishwashers, and microwaves. With spacious floor plans and extra storage, the thoughtfulness of our design shows in every apartment home. Say yes to the style and affordability! Relaxation and convenience are always within reach, from our conference room or theatre room to the fully equipped business center. Our community is pet-friendly, so bring your four-legged companions so they can enjoy these amenities alongside you. As a resident of our Urban Center apartments in Lynnwood, Washington, you'll enjoy the tranquil atmosphere. Take a look at our photo gallery and call us to schedule your personal tour today! PROPERTY FEATURES: − Business Center with Printer − Clubhouse with Kitchen and Free Wifi − Conference and Meeting Room − Controlled Access Entry − Elevators − Pet Waste Stations − Pet-friendly − Private Outdoor Space − Underground Parking − Additional Storage Available − Bark Park − Billiards Parlor − Gated Access − Nearby Shopping and Restaurants − Outdoor Lounge with Barbecue − State-of-the-art Fitness Center − Theater Room PET POLICY: Pets Welcome Upon Approval. Breed restrictions apply. Pet Amenities: Bark Park Dog Wash Station Pet Waste Stations Private Outdoor Space VISIT US TODAY! 15907 Ash Way Lynnwood, WA 98087 Call us today! show contact info Website: www.rentalsapts.com?n=urban_center&rp=p5mpSuykGjM4&t=wb Online Application: www.rentalsapts.com?n=urban_center&rp=p5mpSuykGjM4&t=ap Schedule a Tour: www.rentalsapts.com?n=urban_center&rp=p5mpSuykGjM4&t=sch *The availability of certain amenities may be affected by ongoing preventative maintenance and necessary repair work. All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY 8N62OXBIOTSTVAG",
