        "info": "QR Code Link to This Post 12th Avenue Arts Call us today! show contact info Apartment Details: 1-BR 1-BA | Square Footage: 588 sq ft Monthly Price: $1550 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Lease Length: 12-Month Apartment Features: ● Dishwasher ● Large windows About Our Community: 12th Avenue Arts features 88 affordable apartments, performing arts space, community meeting space, and local retail - all under one roof at 12th and Pine on Capitol Hill. Residents at 12th Avenue Arts enjoy bright, naturally lit apartments, dishwashers in apartment, laundry on every floor, several spacious off-street community patios, and controlled building access. Two theaters and multiple retail stores and restaurants are available in the building for the residents' and neighborhood's enjoyment. The second floor commercial space also houses the main offices of Community Roots Housing. Pet Policy: Pets as well as emotional support, companion, and service animals are allowed in all Community Roots Housing buildings. Some restrictions may apply to certain types of pets. Site managers can answer detailed questions about pet restrictions. Wonderful Amenities: ● Bike storage ● Computer center ● Controlled access ● On-site laundry ● Pet friendly ● Resident lounge ● Resident Services available ● Retail or restaurants in building ● Section 8 vouchers accepted ● Shared courtyard Contact Information: Address: 1660 12th Avenue Seattle, WA 98122 Call us today! show contact info Website: www.rentalsapts.com?n=12th_avenue_arts&rp=bB4MLc9L2rfB&t=wb Online Application: www.rentalsapts.com?n=12th_avenue_arts&rp=bB4MLc9L2rfB&t=ap All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY TOBBM71CT6OSEM",
