        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Welcome to Polaris at Totem Lake! 12333 120th Ave NE Kirkland, WA 98034 Call: show contact info Rental Size: 2 BR - 2 BA - 965 sq ft Monthly Price: $2039 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Lease Length: 6-Month We are an income restricted community. Check our Eligibility tab for information regarding rental criteria Fall in love with where you live at Polaris at Totem Lake in vibrant Kirkland, WA-where modern comfort meets everyday convenience. Ideally located near Totem Lake Village, major employers, dining, and shopping, Polaris offers thoughtfully designed apartment homes with spacious layouts, contemporary finishes, and amenities that support the way you live today. Whether you're unwinding in the comfort of your home or connecting with neighbors in shared community spaces, Polaris at Totem Lake is a place to feel grounded, inspired, and at home. Polaris at Totem Lake proudly welcomes all qualified applicants in accordance with Fair Housing laws. Our community features: ❖ Close to shopping ❖ Elevator ❖ Enclosed Courtyard ❖ Game Room ❖ Interior Playground ❖ Movie Theater ❖ Online Rent Payments ❖ Pet Friendly ❖ Access to public Transportation ❖ Non-Smoking Community ❖ Online Maintenance Portal ❖ On-site Bike Storage ❖ Parking: $150/month Max 1 parking space with limited availability ❖ Picnic Area with BBQ ❖ Some Paid Utilities: Water, Sewer, and Garbage ❖ State-of-the-art Fitness Center Our apartment features: ❖ Dishwasher ❖ Elevator ❖ Freezer ❖ Gated ❖ Grill ❖ Microwave ❖ Oven ❖ Picnic Area ❖ Playground ❖ Smoke Free ❖ Fitness Center ❖ Maintenance on site ❖ Meal Service ❖ Online Services ❖ Property Manager on Site ❖ Recreation Room ❖ Refrigerator ❖ Stainless Steel Appliances ❖ Vinyl Flooring ❖ Washer/Dryer Call: -- show contact info -- Our Pet-Policy: Pet policy: We are pet friendly! Both dogs and cats are allowed! Pets - Max 2 Allowed Refundable Pet Deposit: $250 per household Monthly Pet Rent: $25 per pet The following breed restrictions apply: Pit Bull, Rottweiler, Presa Canario, German Shepherd, Husky, Malamute, Doberman, Chow Chow, St. Bernard, Great Dane, Akita, Staffordshire Terriers, American Bull Dog, Karelian Bear Dog. Exotic Animals: Reptiles, Ferrets, Skunks, Raccoons, Squirrels, Rabbits, Birds, Pigs, Arachnids, Piranha, other farm or poisonous animals. Aquarium max 5 gallons, must be on the first floor, Manage Website: www.lease-apts.com?n=polaris_at_totem_lake&rp=otSsKYg21P4e&t=wb Online Application: www.lease-apts.com?n=polaris_at_totem_lake&rp=otSsKYg21P4e&t=ap 3D Virtual Tour: www.lease-apts.com?n=polaris_at_totem_lake&rp=otSsKYg21P4e&t=trt Schedule a Tour: www.lease-apts.com?n=polaris_at_totem_lake&rp=otSsKYg21P4e&t=sch All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY Z5M6J36KXEZX2R53",
