        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Highlands West Shoreline Visit our community today! 18520 8th Ave NW Shoreline, WA 98177 Call for details: show contact info Monthly Price: $1900 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Apartment Type: 1-BR 1-BA Apartment Size: 750 sq ft Lease Terms: 12-Month Pet Policy: Pets Welcome Upon Approval. Maximum adult weight is 25 pounds. Call office for details. What you'll find in our community: ➢ Access to Exercise Room ➢ Beautiful Landscaping ➢ Community Room ➢ Large Screen TV ➢ Maintenance Emergency on-call ➢ On-site Office Staff ➢ Public Parks Nearby ➢ Set in a Garden Setting with Koi Pond ➢ Shimmering Swimming Pool ➢ Smoke-free Community Description: Highlands West Apartments in Shoreline, Washington, exclusively for individuals aged 55 and better, proudly maintains a smoke-free environment. We're conveniently located just 5 minutes away from the picturesque Richmond Beach and park. Residents can easily access the Senior Center via a nearby bus stop, and there are also pet parks in close proximity. Additionally, within a short 4-minute walk, residents can find various amenities, including Starbucks, QFS grocery, and diverse dining options such as Mexican, Thai, Teriyaki, and Greek restaurants. There's also a bank, dry cleaner, coffee shop, and small convenience store for added convenience. Enjoy the peace of the Richmond Beach area is quiet 55 Plus Community. Walking distance to grocery shopping, local restaurants and a short 10 minute drive to Richmond Beach itself. Highlands & Highlands West Apartments are just a great place to live. Call today or stop by to schedule a tour. This apartment comes with: ➢ Dishwasher ➢ Extra Large Windows ➢ Freezer ➢ Heating ➢ Kitchen ➢ Oven ➢ Pantry ➢ Range ➢ Refrigerator ➢ Smoke Free Call for details: show contact info Mon - Fri: 8:00 AM - 5:00 PM Visit our website to schedule a personal tour! Website: www.lease-apts.com?n=highlands_west_shoreline&rp=jK7i6qKCzQQy&t=wb Online Application: www.lease-apts.com?n=highlands_west_shoreline&rp=jK7i6qKCzQQy&t=ap Schedule a Tour: www.lease-apts.com?n=highlands_west_shoreline&rp=jK7i6qKCzQQy&t=sch All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY 884L00EL2DKJDO7",
