        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Welcome home to Highlands West Shoreline! Located at: 18520 8th Ave NW Shoreline, WA 98177 Rental Information: # of Bedrooms: 1 # of Bathrooms: 1 Square Footage: 750 sq ft Monthly Price: $1900 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Contact: show contact info Highlands West Apartments in Shoreline, Washington, exclusively for individuals aged 55 and better, proudly maintains a smoke-free environment. We're conveniently located just 5 minutes away from the picturesque Richmond Beach and park. Residents can easily access the Senior Center via a nearby bus stop, and there are also pet parks in close proximity. Additionally, within a short 4-minute walk, residents can find various amenities, including Starbucks, QFS grocery, and diverse dining options such as Mexican, Thai, Teriyaki, and Greek restaurants. There's also a bank, dry cleaner, coffee shop, and small convenience store for added convenience. Enjoy the peace of the Richmond Beach area is quiet 55 Plus Community. Walking distance to grocery shopping, local restaurants and a short 10 minute drive to Richmond Beach itself. Highlands & Highlands West Apartments are just a great place to live. Call today or stop by to schedule a tour. Community Features: ❖ Access to Exercise Room ❖ Beautiful Landscaping ❖ Community Room ❖ Large Screen TV ❖ Maintenance Emergency on-call ❖ On-site Office Staff ❖ Public Parks Nearby ❖ Set in a Garden Setting with Koi Pond ❖ Shimmering Swimming Pool ❖ Smoke-free Community Apartment Home Features: ❖ Dishwasher ❖ Extra Large Windows ❖ Freezer ❖ Heating ❖ Kitchen ❖ Oven ❖ Pantry ❖ Range ❖ Refrigerator ❖ Smoke Free Office Hours: Mon - Fri: 8:00 AM - 5:00 PM Contact: show contact info Pet Policy: Pets Welcome Upon Approval. Maximum adult weight is 25 pounds. Call office for details. Leasing Options: 12-Month Website: www.leaseaptsnow.com?n=highlands_west_shoreline&rp=9LNk3jqm9Y1d&t=wb Online Application: www.leaseaptsnow.com?n=highlands_west_shoreline&rp=9LNk3jqm9Y1d&t=ap Schedule a Tour: www.leaseaptsnow.com?n=highlands_west_shoreline&rp=9LNk3jqm9Y1d&t=sch All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY 884L00EL2DKJDO7",
