        "info": "QR Code Link to This Post RENTAL INFO Monthly Price: $2050- $2649 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. The Trail Apartments: 627 Avenue A Snohomish, WA 98290 Apartment for Rent: 1 - 3-BR 1 - 2-BA | Square Feet: 625 - 1140 sq ft | Lease Length: Variable Contact Info: show contact info PROPERTY AMENITIES ❖ Assigned Parking ❖ Barbecue Area ❖ Basketball Court ❖ Emergency Maintenance ❖ On-Line Payments ❖ Pet Friendly ❖ Playground ❖ Recycling ❖ Remodeled ❖ Storage ❖ Ideal Location in Snohomish ❖ Near Restaurants and Shops ❖ On-Site Maintenance ❖ On-Site Management APARTMENT AMENITIES ❖ Cable Ready ❖ Carpeting ❖ Dishwasher ❖ Pull Down Faucet ❖ Refrigerator ❖ Spacious Living Areas ❖ Updated Kitchen ❖ Vinyl Flooring ❖ Washer/Dryer ❖ Window Coverings ADDITIONAL INFO Description: \"Currently fully leased. Accepting inquiries for future available units.\" The Trail Apartments is your ideal home base for living, working and exploring in Snohomish, WA. Perfectly situated on a tree-lined avenue in a classic Snohomish neighborhood, our homes offer all the comfort and convenience you could ever desire. Just a few blocks away is historic downtown Snohomish, home of an endless array of antiques shops, Victorian homes and storefronts, quaint coffee shops and trendy restaurants. Pet Policy: 2 pets per apartment home No weight limit $50 pet rent per pet $400 refundable deposit, $200 pet fee ($300 for 2 pets) The following breed restrictions apply - Akita, Alaskan Malamute, Chow, Dalmatian, Doberman Pinscher, German Shepherd, Great Dane, Husky, Rottweiler, Saint Bernard, Wolf Dog Hybrids and all Pit Bull breeds. Website: www.leaseaptsnow.com?n=trail&rp=cAprLjEFniKe&t=wb 3D Virtual Tour: www.leaseaptsnow.com?n=trail&rp=cAprLjEFniKe&t=trt Schedule a Tour: www.leaseaptsnow.com?n=trail&rp=cAprLjEFniKe&t=sch Contact Info: show contact info Photos are representational only. Actual home may have small changes. All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY N3MEDI0TDB86Z05E",
