        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Community Location: 29 St. Helens Ave - Tacoma, WA 98402 Monthly Price: $1325 - $1563 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Apartment Details: 1 Bedroom 1 Bath | 525 sq ft Leasing Options: 6-Month, 7-Month, 8-Month, 9-Month, 10-Month, 11-Month, 12-Month Reach out via phone: show contact info Apartment Amenities: ❖ 1 and 2 Bedroom Apartment Homes and Penthouses ❖ 16 Floors of Spectacular Views of Commencement Bay* ❖ Dishwasher ❖ Disposal Chutes ❖ Fully-equipped Kitchen ❖ High Speed Internet Access ❖ Oven/Range ❖ Refrigerator/Freezer ❖ Vinyl Flooring ❖ Wood-look Plank Flooring ❖ 16 Floors of Spectacular Views of Commencement Bay in Select Units ❖ Electronic Thermostat ❖ Heating ❖ Large Closets ❖ Stainless Steel Appliances ❖ Views ❖ Wood-look Plank Flooring Property Features: ❖ 24-Hour Clothes Care Center ❖ Business Center/Clubhouse/Gameroom ❖ Fitness Center ❖ Indoor/Outdoor Lounges ❖ Outdoor Patios & Grill Station ❖ Pet Waste Stations ❖ Recycling ❖ Renters Insurance Program ❖ Smoke Free ❖ Sundeck ❖ 1,500 Sq. Foot Residential Lounge with Stunning Views & Complimentary Wi-Fi ❖ 24-Hour On-site Emergency Maintenance ❖ Controlled Access Bicycle Storage with Work Bench ❖ Immediate Access to Wright Park and Seymour Conservatory - Voted \"Best Place to Relax\" in Tacoma ❖ Package Service ❖ Planned Social Activities ❖ Rentable Storage is Available in the Community with Varying Sizes ❖ Reserved Garage Parking in Secured Building ❖ Waterfront ❖ Yoga Studio Description: Located in the heart of Tacoma, WA's Stadium District, Orion is a renovated high-rise community with panoramic views of Mt. Rainier, Puget Sound, Wright Park, and the desirable New Tacoma city lights. Enjoy living in New Tacoma, surrounded by many restaurants, bars, coffee shops, and local parks nearby. Orion also offers convenient access to Tacoma Link Light Rail and Interstates 705 and 5. Pets: Pet policy: We are pet friendly! Both dogs and cats are allowed! Pets - Max 2 Allowed Pet Deposit: $250 per pet One-time Pet Fee: $250 per pet Monthly Pet Rent: $35 per pet We do not have a weight limit. Reach out via phone: show contact info Website: www.lease-apts.com?n=orion&rp=fZi2hRXyaeG5&t=wb Online Application: www.lease-apts.com?n=orion&rp=fZi2hRXyaeG5&t=ap Schedule a Tour: www.lease-apts.com?n=orion&rp=fZi2hRXyaeG5&t=sch Availability and pricing are subject to change daily All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY 3V1JC2ID9CJTRSC1",
