        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Sterling Ridge 11328 SE Kent-Kangley Road Kent, WA 98030 Call our office at show contact info Look & Lease Special! Tour and lease within 2 weeks - get 1 month free! Tour and lease within 1 month - get 2 weeks free!* *Restrictions apply, offer valid on select units . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . Rental Size: 2 BR - 2 BA - 930 sq ft Monthly Price: $2110 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Lease Length: 6-Month, 7-Month, 8-Month, 9-Month, 10-Month, 11-Month, 12-Month . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . If you are looking for superior living, then look no further - you've found it at Sterling Ridge! Our beautiful community is perfectly nestled in Kent, Washington. Conveniently located with close proximity to Highway 167 and Interstate 5, you're just minutes away from shopping, dining, and entertainment. Let Sterling Ridge be your gateway to fun and excitement in Kent, WA! Our spacious and inviting apartments are designed with your comfort in mind. Choose from one, two, and three bedroom floor plans that are loaded with features, including an all-electric kitchen, balcony or patio, vaulted ceilings, and walk-in closets. A cozy wood burning fireplace tops it all off. Sterling Ridge has everything you have ever dreamed about in a home! Great apartment home living doesn't have to end when you leave your front door, which is why we've tailored our community around you. We are proud to feature a relaxing clubhouse, play area, beautifully landscaped grounds, and more. Part-time courtesy patrol and on-site maintenance ensure all of our residents feel at ease and at home. Our commitment to your comfort and quality of life is second to none. Visit today and see what makes Sterling Ridge the perfect place to call home. Schedule a Tour: https://www.liveatsterlingridge.com/?utm_knock=cl&doorway=schedule . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . Features and Amenities: ➢ Access to Public Transportation ➢ Amazon Hub ➢ Assigned Parking ➢ Barbecue Area Coming Soon ➢ Cable Available ➢ Clubhouse ➢ Easy Access to Freeways, Shopping, and Dining ➢ Fenced Lot ➢ Fitness Center ➢ Lush Landscaped Grounds ➢ Neighborhood ➢ On-call Maintenance ➢ One, Two and Three Bedroom Floor Plans ➢ Online Services ➢ Part-time Courtesy Patrol ➢ Play Area ➢ Public Parks Nearby ➢ Recycling ➢ Renters Insurance Program ➢ Smoke Free . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . This Apartment Home Comes With: ➢ Balcony or Patio ➢ Cable Ready ➢ Carpeted Floors ➢ Disability Access in Select Apartment Homes ➢ Disposal ➢ Extra Storage ➢ Fully-equipped Kitchen ➢ Heating ➢ High-speed Internet Access ➢ Large Bedrooms ➢ Linen Closet ➢ Pantry ➢ Range w/Oven ➢ Refrigerator ➢ Vertical Blinds ➢ Vinyl Flooring ➢ Walk-in Closets ➢ Warming Drawer ➢ Window Coverings ➢ Wood-burning Fireplace . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . Call our office at -- show contact info -- Website: www.apts-rental.com?n=sterling_ridge&rp=uiUTYVfe3WDN&t=wb Online Application: www.apts-rental.com?n=sterling_ridge&rp=uiUTYVfe3WDN&t=ap Schedule a Tour: www.apts-rental.com?n=sterling_ridge&rp=uiUTYVfe3WDN&t=sch Pets: Pets Welcome Upon Approval. Limit of 2 pets per home. Pets must not exceed 25 pounds. A $250 pet fee and $250 non-refundable deposit per pet apply. There will be a $25 monthly pet rent charged per pet. Breed restrictions apply.