        "info": "QR Code Link to This Post Sterling Ridge Visit our community today! 11328 SE Kent-Kangley Road Kent, WA 98030 Call: show contact info Look & Lease Special! Tour and lease within 2 weeks - get 1 month free! Tour and lease within 1 month - get 2 weeks free!* *Restrictions apply, offer valid on select units Monthly Price: $1770 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Apartment Type: 1-BR 1-BA Apartment Size: 720 sq ft Lease Terms: 6-Month, 7-Month, 8-Month, 9-Month, 10-Month, 11-Month, 12-Month Pet Policy: Pets Welcome Upon Approval. Limit of 2 pets per home. Pets must not exceed 25 pounds. A $250 pet fee and $250 non-refundable deposit per pet apply. There will be a $25 monthly pet rent charged per pet. Breed restrictions apply. What you'll find in our community: ◾ Access to Public Transportation ◾ Amazon Hub ◾ Assigned Parking ◾ Barbecue Area Coming Soon ◾ Cable Available ◾ Clubhouse ◾ Easy Access to Freeways, Shopping, and Dining ◾ Fenced Lot ◾ Fitness Center ◾ Lush Landscaped Grounds ◾ Neighborhood ◾ On-call Maintenance ◾ One, Two and Three Bedroom Floor Plans ◾ Online Services ◾ Part-time Courtesy Patrol ◾ Play Area ◾ Public Parks Nearby ◾ Recycling ◾ Renters Insurance Program ◾ Smoke Free Description: Great apartment home living doesn't have to end when you leave your front door, which is why we've tailored our community around you. We are proud to feature a relaxing clubhouse, play area, beautifully landscaped grounds, and more. Part-time courtesy patrol and on-site maintenance ensure all of our residents feel at ease and at home. Our commitment to your comfort and quality of life is second to none. Visit today and see what makes Sterling Ridge the perfect place to call home. Schedule a Tour: https://www.liveatsterlingridge.com/?utm_knock=cl&doorway=schedule This apartment comes with: ◾ Balcony or Patio ◾ Cable Ready ◾ Carpeted Floors ◾ Disability Access in Select Apartment Homes ◾ Disposal ◾ Extra Storage ◾ Fully-equipped Kitchen ◾ Heating ◾ High-speed Internet Access ◾ Large Bedrooms ◾ Linen Closet ◾ Pantry ◾ Range w/Oven ◾ Refrigerator ◾ Vertical Blinds ◾ Vinyl Flooring ◾ Walk-in Closets ◾ Warming Drawer ◾ Window Coverings ◾ Wood-burning Fireplace Call: show contact info Mon - Fri: 9:00 AM - 5:00 PM Visit our website to schedule a personal tour! Website: www.leaseaptsnow.com?n=sterling_ridge&rp=cD3i66n2dKTc&t=wb Online Application: www.leaseaptsnow.com?n=sterling_ridge&rp=cD3i66n2dKTc&t=ap Schedule a Tour: www.leaseaptsnow.com?n=sterling_ridge&rp=cD3i66n2dKTc&t=sch Availability and pricing are subject to change daily All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY T7V6O44MXZNOJ93Z5",
