est Parking ✓ King County - Housing Vouchers Welcome ✓ Large Dogs Allowed ✓ Mail Locker ✓ Night Patrol ✓ On-line Maintenance Request CONTACT US TODAY! Foster Commons 5700 S 129th Street Seattle, WA 98178 Mon: 9:00 AM - 5:00 PM Tue: 9:30 AM - 5:00 PM Wed - Fri: 9:00 AM - 5:00 PM Call for details: show contact info Website: www.rentalsapts.com?n=foster_commons&rp=1taXPRnSQknY&t=wb Online Application: www.rentalsapts.com?n=foster_commons&rp=1taXPRnSQknY&t=ap Schedule a Tour: www.rentalsapts.com?n=foster_commons&rp=1taXPRnSQknY&t=sch All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY 52VK5OMH1ZIS1N2A",
