        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post 2 Bedroom 1 Bathroom | 850 sq ft Monthly Price: $1800 - $2018 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Woodhaven 4632 Fowler Ave Everett, WA 98203 Contact our leasing office at show contact info Description: From designer updates like faux wood flooring, quartz countertops, shaker-style cabinets, and conveniences like on-site storage and laundry facilities, explore our homes and see the joys of home at Woodhaven. A robust setting and friendly staff welcome you - we love your furry friends too! Enjoy the large pet park, community garden, playground, and much more. Apartment Amenities: ➢ Carpeting ➢ Ceiling Fans ➢ Heating ➢ Linen Closet ➢ Oven ➢ Patio/Balcony in Most Units ➢ Range ➢ Refrigerator ➢ Smoke Free ➢ Tub/Shower ➢ Built-in Bookshelves ➢ Cable Ready ➢ Crown Molding ➢ Dishwasher ➢ Double Pane Windows ➢ Faux Wood Flooring ➢ Granite Countertops ➢ Upgraded Interiors ➢ Vinyl Flooring ➢ Window Covering Our Residents Enjoy: ➢ 24 Hour Maintenance ➢ BBQ/Picnic Area ➢ Beautiful Landscaping ➢ Community Garden ➢ Cornhole ➢ Courtyard ➢ Laundry Facilities ➢ Off Street Parking ➢ Online Services ➢ Easy Access to Historic Downtown Everett ➢ Minutes from Everett Naval Station ➢ Pet Friendly ➢ Pet Play Area ➢ Playground ➢ Property Manager on Site ➢ Renters Insurance Program ➢ Secluded Forest Park Location ➢ Shuffleboard ➢ Storage Units for Rent Additional Details: Deposit: Call Terms: 6-Month, 8-Month, 9-Month, 10-Month, 12-Month Pets: 2 pets per apartment home $50 pet rent per pet $400 deposit per pet $200 non-refundable deposit for 1st pet, $250 for additional pet The following breed restrictions apply - Akita, Alaskan Malamute, Chow, Dalmatian, Doberman Pinscher, German Shepherd, Great Dane, Husky, Rottweiler, Saint Bernard, Wolf Dog Hybrids and all Pit Bull breeds. Contact our leasing office at show contact info Website: www.rentalsapts.com?n=woodhaven&rp=v7S61jZT82M4&t=wb Online Application: www.rentalsapts.com?n=woodhaven&rp=v7S61jZT82M4&t=ap 3D Virtual Tour: www.rentalsapts.com?n=woodhaven&rp=v7S61jZT82M4&t=trt Schedule a Tour: www.rentalsapts.com?n=woodhaven&rp=v7S61jZT82M4&t=sch All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY 6866967C5B3149B",
