        "mainpic": "c536b2b8-3ea8-4fe8-b0a1-6f0bee48872d",
        "msg": "QR Code Link to This Post Hillview Apartments 12816 60th Lane South C-11 Seattle, WA 98178 Call our office at show contact info . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . Rental Size: 2 BR - 1.5 BA - 890 sq ft Monthly Price: $1680 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Lease Length: 12-Month . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . FREE RENT!! Now Available!! 2 Bed/1.5 Bath with IN UNIT LAUNDRY 2 bd, 1.5 ba | Available Now Looking for more than just an apartment_ Discover why Hillview Apartments was recently nominated by The Seattle Times for Best Apartment Community in the Pacific Northwest. Our thoughtfully designed one-bedroom homes offer approximately 890 square feet of comfortable living space, with the features that make everyday life easier and more enjoyable. Each home includes: • Full-size washer and dryer in every apartment • Private balcony with additional storage space • Cozy wood-burning fireplace • Reserved parking • Pet-friendly community with an on-site dog area Nestled among mature evergreens between Seattle and Renton, Hillview offers the convenience of city access with the comfort of a neighborhood feel. Located directly on the King County Metro route, commuting to downtown Seattle, Renton, Tukwila, or SeaTac is simple and convenient. At Hillview, we're continually investing in our community through ongoing improvements and resident-focused enhancements. Combined with seasonal events and a welcoming atmosphere, it's easy to see why our residents are proud to call Hillview home. Diversity • Connection • Community Come experience the difference of an award-nominated community and find your place at Hillview Apartments. Schedule your tour today! Leas