se Details: $1680 Rent $170 Water/Sewage/Garbage $200 Admin/Hold Fee $600 Refundable Deposit $66 Application Fee - Here is the link to apply: www.lease-apts.com?n=hillview&rp=by2DjAz1TtmM&t=sch - Cosigner Link: https://apply.alliance2020.com/#/view/wj8m *Please note when applying to select all other cities as we are unincorporated King County and not City of Seattle Virtual tour - https://www. /view-3d-home/b20e6dba-b4ce-4e9b-96ed-af1c8e849e8d_setAttribution=mls&wl=true&utm_source=dashboard We do not accept comprehensive reusable tenant screening reports as defined by and pursuant to RCW 59.18. Icon Real Estate Services is an equal opportunity housing provider who commits to complying with all federal, state, and local fair housing laws. We will not discriminate against any person based on race, color, religion, national origin, sex (including gender identity and sexual orientation), familial status, disability, or any other protected classes specified by applicable laws. All applicants are scored on the same standards; one person, group, or family at a time on a first-come, first-served basis. All vacancies will be filled by the first qualified applicant who can move in closest to the availability date Amenities Dishwasher Balcony w/Storage Nightly Security Patrol New mail/parcel boxes Community Courtyard Assigned Parking Landscaping Services On-Site Maintenance On-Site Property Manager Dog Park In Unit Laundry King County Bus Line Easy Access to I-5 CCTV Pet Friendly Up to 50 lbs Rental Terms Rent: $1,680 Application Fee: $66 Security Deposit: $800 Available Now Pet Policy Cats allowed Small dogs allowed Utilities Water Sewer Garbage Recycling Appliances Refrigerator Dishwasher Garbage Disposal Stove/Oven Washer and Dryer . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . Features and Amenities: . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . 