        "info": "QR Code Link to This Post Larned Monthly Price: $1476 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. SIZE: 300 sq ft BEDROOMS: 1 BATHROOMS: 1 LEASE TERMS: 12-Month Call for details: show contact info APARTMENT HOME FEATURES: Welcome to Larned, a residential community featuring studio and one bedroom apartments in Seattle, WA. Spacious layouts and amenities welcome you home, along with exceptional service and an ideal location within walking distance to shopping, dining and entertainment options. Are you looking for an apartment for rent in Seattle, WA? Contact our friendly, professional office staff to schedule a tour today. PROPERTY FEATURES: ➢ Bike storage ➢ Classic building ➢ Controlled access ➢ On-site laundry ➢ Pet friendly ➢ Resident Services available ➢ Section 8 vouchers accepted ➢ Storage available PET POLICY: Number of pets allowed: 2 Pets as well as emotional support, companion, and service animals are allowed in all Community Roots Housing buildings. Some restrictions may apply to certain types of pets. Site managers can answer detailed questions about pet restrictions.. VISIT US TODAY! 2030 7th Ave Seattle, WA 98121 Call for details: show contact info Website: www.rentalsapts.com?n=larned&rp=eqo1qvJNJ5Gq&t=wb All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY 2JEVV0NM7M1OLH",
