        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Welcome to Fleming Apartments! 2321 4th Ave Seattle, WA 98121 Phone Number: show contact info Rental Size: 1 - 1 BR - 1 BA - 397 - 552 sq ft Monthly Price: $1050 - $1300 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Lease Length: 12-Month \"Currently fully leased. Accepting inquiries for future available units.\" At Fleming, you'll discover everything you need to live the convenient and carefree lifestyle you deserve. If you're looking to find your next home in Seattle, WA, contact us today. Your next home is waiting for you here at Fleming, a charming community of studio and one bedroom apartments located near the heart of Seattle, WA. Inside these spacious floor plans, you'll discover cozy interiors complete with all the modern conveniences you desire. Outside your apartment, the community's inviting amenities provide the perfect opportunity to relax and enjoy the company of neighbors. As a resident of Fleming, you'll also enjoy easy access to the area's most popular shopping, dining, and entertainment destinations. Reach out today for more information. Our community features: ❖ Classic building ❖ Community patios ❖ On-site laundry ❖ Pet friendly ❖ Controlled access ❖ Resident Services available ❖ Section 8 vouchers accepted ❖ Walk up ramp to all floors Our apartment features: ❖ Central heat included ❖ Heating ❖ Kitchen ❖ Paid water/sewer/garbage Phone Number: -- show contact info -- Our Pet-Policy: Number of pets allowed: 2 Pets as well as emotional support, companion, and service animals are allowed in all Community Roots Housing buildings. Some restrictions may apply to certain types of pets. Site managers can answer detailed questions about pet restrictions.. Website: www.leaseaptsnow.com?n=fleming&rp=myPrTa4eQKg6&t=wb All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY T0OMHT6I2BGOCI8X",
