        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Polaris at Totem Lake 12333 120th Ave NE Kirkland, WA 98034 Monthly Price: $1941 - $2350 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Bedrooms: 3 Bathrooms: 2 Square Footage: 1226 sq ft Call to schedule a viewing: show contact info We are an income restricted community. Check our Eligibility tab for information regarding rental criteria Features in this apartment home: ❖ Carpet ❖ Concierge ❖ Courtyard ❖ Dishwasher ❖ Gameroom ❖ Gated ❖ Heating ❖ Oven ❖ Smoke Free ❖ Tub/Shower ❖ 24 Hour Access ❖ Business Center ❖ Ceiling Fans ❖ Fitness Center ❖ Media Center/Movie Theatre ❖ Online Services ❖ Public Transportation ❖ Refrigerator ❖ Washer/Dryer ❖ Window Coverings About the community: Discover the heart of community living at Polaris at Totem Lake in Kirkland, WA. Here, neighbors become friends and shared spaces-from inviting resident lounges to thoughtfully designed outdoor areas-are created to bring people together. With a warm, welcoming atmosphere and a true sense of connection, Polaris at Totem Lake sets the stage for meaningful moments and everyday comfort. Whether you're hosting a casual weekend gathering or enjoying a peaceful walk around the neighborhood, this is a place where you can truly feel at home. Come be a part of something special. Your community awaits. Amenities at our property: ❖ Close to shopping ❖ Elevator ❖ Enclosed Courtyard ❖ Game Room ❖ Interior Playground ❖ Movie Theater ❖ Online Rent Payments ❖ Pet Friendly ❖ Access to public Transportation ❖ Non-Smoking Community ❖ Online Maintenance Portal ❖ On-site Bike Storage ❖ Parking: $150/month Max 1 parking space with limited availability ❖ Picnic Area with BBQ ❖ Some Paid Utilities: Water, Sewer, and Garbage ❖ State-of-the-art Fitness Center Additional information: Call to schedule a viewing: show contact info Terms: 6-Month Pets: Pet policy: We are pet friendly! Both dogs and cats are allowed! Pets - Max 2 Allowed Refundable Pet Deposit: $250 per household Monthly Pet Rent: $25 per pet The following breed restrictions apply: Pit Bull, Rottweiler, Presa Canario, German Shepherd, Husky, Malamute, Doberman, Chow Chow, St. Bernard, Great Dane, Akita, Staffordshire Terriers, American Bull Dog, Karelian Bear Dog. Exotic Animals: Reptiles, Ferrets, Skunks, Raccoons, Squirrels, Rabbits, Birds, Pigs, Arachnids, Piranha, other farm or poisonous animals. Aquarium max 5 gallons, must be on the first floor, Manage Website: www.rentalsapts.com?n=polaris_at_totem_lake&rp=p7L91ymWSkWu&t=wb Online Application: www.rentalsapts.com?n=polaris_at_totem_lake&rp=p7L91ymWSkWu&t=ap 3D Virtual Tour: www.rentalsapts.com?n=polaris_at_totem_lake&rp=p7L91ymWSkWu&t=trt Schedule a Tour: www.rentalsapts.com?n=polaris_at_totem_lake&rp=p7L91ymWSkWu&t=sch All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY Z2JHI7O0G9H4K5HL",
