        "msg": "QR Code Link to This Post Devonshire Apartments Located at: 420 Wall St Seattle, WA 98121 Featured apartment home: 1 bed | 1 bath | 471 sq ft Monthly Price: $1438 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Phone: show contact info This three-story 1920s' brick building is located on Wall Street between Fourth and Fifth Avenues. The Devonshire underwent a full-scale renovation that was completed in 2024. The restoration spanned a broad scope of work, including all new mechanical, electrical, and plumbing systems. Apartment interiors were outfitted with LED lighting, new stainless steel appliances, fresh kitchen and bathroom cabinet packages, new doors, and high-performance glass. New exterior wall insulation, roof insulation, and fresh windows enhanced energy efficiency and interior climate control, while also dramatically reducing the impact of street noise. Energy recovery ventilators were installed to further improve ventilation and provide a healthier interior air environment for residents. Wonderful Amenities! − Classic Building − Controlled Access − On-site Laundry − Paid parking available (Please inquire for availability and cost) − Paid Water/Sewer/Garbage − Community amenities coming soon! − Pet Friendly − Resident Services Available − Section 8 Vouchers Accepted − Shared Courtyard Apartment Features! Application fee waived when application completed at time of tour Hours: Mon - Sun: - Phone: show contact info Website: www.rentalsapts.com?n=devonshire&rp=vegPdi5vPqWA&t=wb Online Application: www.rentalsapts.com?n=devonshire&rp=vegPdi5vPqWA&t=ap Terms: 12-Month Pet Policy: Pets as well as emotional support, companion, and service animals are allowed in all Community Roots Housing buildings. Some restrictions may apply to certain types of pets. Site managers can answer detailed questions about pet restrictions. All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change with