        "geocode_query": "29 St. Helens Ave",
        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post The Orion 29 St. Helens Ave Tacoma, WA 98402 Call: show contact info . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . Rental Size: 1 BR - 1 BA - 525 sq ft Monthly Price: $1450 - $1619 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Lease Length: 6-Month, 7-Month, 8-Month, 9-Month, 10-Month, 11-Month, 12-Month . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . Our modern amenities collection includes a 24-hour fitness facility & yoga studio, cinema room, clothes care center, online rent payment, a rooftop terrace, and a 1,500 sq. ft. community room with a contemporary kitchen and complimentary wi-fi. We welcome you to experience life on a higher level in our refreshed, urban community. . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . Features and Amenities: ✓ Business Center/Clubhouse/Gameroom ✓ Elevator ✓ Fitness Center ✓ Indoor/Outdoor Lounges ✓ Laundry Facilities ✓ Outdoor Patios & Grill Station ✓ Pet Waste Stations ✓ Renters Insurance Program ✓ Smoke Free ✓ Sundeck ✓ 24-Hour On-site Emergency Maintenance ✓ Controlled Access Bicycle Storage with Work Bench ✓ Historic Building ✓ Immediate Access to Wright Park and Seymour Conservatory - Voted \"Best Place to Relax\" in Tacoma ✓ Online Services ✓ Package Service ✓ Planned Social Activities ✓ Reserved Garage Parking in Secured Building ✓ Waterfront ✓ Yoga Studio . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . This Apartment Home Comes With: ✓ 16 Floors of Spectacular Views of Commencement Bay* ✓ Carpeting ✓ Dishwasher ✓ Disposal Chutes ✓ Elevator(s) ✓ Fully-equipped Kitchen ✓ High Speed Internet Access ✓ Vinyl Flooring ✓ Window Coverings ✓ Wood-look Plank Flooring ✓ 16 Floors of Spectacular Views of Commencement Bay in Select Units ✓ Electronic Thermostat ✓ Heating ✓ Large Closets ✓ Stainless Steel Appliances ✓ Views ✓ Wood-look Plank Flooring . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . Call: -- show contact info -- Website: www.apt-rental.com?n=orion&rp=vLXNBHYnz68S&t=wb Online Application: www.apt-rental.com?n=orion&rp=vLXNBHYnz68S&t=ap Schedule a Tour: www.apt-rental.com?n=orion&rp=vLXNBHYnz68S&t=sch Pets: Pet policy: We are pet friendly! Both dogs and cats are allowed! Pets - Max 2 Allowed Pet Deposit: $250 per pet One-time Pet Fee: $250 per pet Monthly Pet Rent: $35 per pet We do not have a weight limit. . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . Availability and pricing are subject to change daily All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY C0SMGAER06TNOKB",
