asher ✓ Disposal Chutes ✓ Elevator(s) ✓ Fully-equipped Kitchen ✓ High Speed Internet Access ✓ Vinyl Flooring ✓ Window Coverings ✓ Wood-look Plank Flooring ✓ 16 Floors of Spectacular Views of Commencement Bay in Select Units ✓ Electronic Thermostat ✓ Heating ✓ Large Closets ✓ Stainless Steel Appliances ✓ Views ✓ Wood-look Plank Flooring . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . Call: -- show contact info -- Website: www.apt-rental.com?n=orion&rp=vLXNBHYnz68S&t=wb Online Application: www.apt-rental.com?n=orion&rp=vLXNBHYnz68S&t=ap Schedule a Tour: www.apt-rental.com?n=orion&rp=vLXNBHYnz68S&t=sch Pets: Pet policy: We are pet friendly! Both dogs and cats are allowed! Pets - Max 2 Allowed Pet Deposit: $250 per pet One-time Pet Fee: $250 per pet Monthly Pet Rent: $35 per pet We do not have a weight limit. . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . Availability and pricing are subject to change daily All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY C0SMGAER06TNOKB",
