        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post The Orion - A place to call home! Bed: 2 / Bath: 1 Sq. Footage: 650 sq ft Monthly Price: $1999 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Terms: 6-Month, 7-Month, 8-Month, 9-Month, 10-Month, 11-Month, 12-Month Contact us for more information! show contact info Our modern amenities collection includes a 24-hour fitness facility & yoga studio, cinema room, clothes care center, online rent payment, a rooftop terrace, and a 1,500 sq. ft. community room with a contemporary kitchen and complimentary wi-fi. We welcome you to experience life on a higher level in our refreshed, urban community. Our Apartment Homes Feature: − 1 and 2 Bedroom Apartment Homes and Penthouses − 16 Floors of Spectacular Views of Commencement Bay* − Cable Ready − Dishwasher − Disposal Chutes − Elevator(s) − Fully-equipped Kitchen − High Speed Internet Access − Window Coverings − Wood-look Plank Flooring − 16 Floors of Spectacular Views of Commencement Bay in Select Units − Electronic Thermostat − Heating − Large Closets − Stainless Steel Appliances − Views − Wood-look Plank Flooring Our Residents Enjoy: − 24-Hour Clothes Care Center − Business Center/Clubhouse/Gameroom − Elevator − Fitness Center − Indoor/Outdoor Lounges − Laundry Facilities − Outdoor Patios & Grill Station − Pet Waste Stations − Smoke Free − Sundeck − 1,500 Sq. Foot Residential Lounge with Stunning Views & Complimentary Wi-Fi − 24-Hour On-site Emergency Maintenance − Bocce Ball Court − Historic Building − Immediate Access to Wright Park and Seymour Conservatory - Voted \"Best Place to Relax\" in Tacoma − Online Services − Package Service − Planned Social Activities − Waterfront − Yoga Studio Contact us for more information! show contact info 29 St. Helens Ave Tacoma, WA 98402 Website: www.rentalsapts.com?n=orion&rp=tgoP3qVMjfAs&t=wb Online Application: www.rentalsapts.com?n=orion&rp=tgoP3qVMjfAs&t=ap Schedule a Tour: www.rentalsapts.com?n=orion&rp=tgoP3qVMjfAs&t=sch Mon - Fri: 9:00 AM - 6:00 PM Pets: Pet policy: We are pet friendly! Both dogs and cats are allowed! Pets - Max 2 Allowed Pet Deposit: $250 per pet One-time Pet Fee: $250 per pet Monthly Pet Rent: $35 per pet We do not have a weight limit. Availability and pricing are subject to change daily All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY SI3X2VK4KO5X3T",
