        "msg": "QR Code Link to This Post Highlands West Shoreline, located at 18520 8th Ave NW Shoreline, WA 98177. Call us at show contact info Description ........ Experience ultimate comfort in our spacious one and two bedroom apartments for rent, equipped with everything you need. Enjoy panoramic views through extra-large windows that bring the outdoors in. Stay cozy during winter with fireplaces in select homes. Plus, relish outdoor moments on our large decks! Our residents can access various amenities, including a community room to socialize with neighbors. They can also maintain their fitness at our state-of-the-art fitness center. Additionally, they can relax and appreciate the scenic views of the Koi pond. Call our office today and schedule a tour of Highlands West Apartments in Shoreline, WA! Enjoy the peace of the Richmond Beach area is quiet 55 Plus Community. Walking distance to grocery shopping, local restaurants and a short 10 minute drive to Richmond Beach itself. Highlands & Highlands West Apartments are just a great place to live. Call today or stop by to schedule a tour. Bedrooms ........... 1 Bathrooms ......... 1 Sq Footage ......... 750 sq ft Monthly Price: $1900 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Lease Term ........ 12-Month Amenity List ...... ✓ Access to Exercise Room ✓ Beautiful Landscaping ✓ Community Room ✓ Large Screen TV ✓ Maintenance Emergency on-call ✓ On-site Office Staff ✓ Public Parks Nearby ✓ Set in a Garden Setting with Koi Pond ✓ Shimmering Swimming Pool ✓ Smoke-free Community Apartment Home Features ..... ✓ Dishwasher ✓ Extra Large Windows ✓ Freezer ✓ Heating ✓ Kitchen ✓ Oven ✓ Pantry ✓ Range ✓ Refrigerator ✓ Smoke Free Our Pet Policy ... Pets Welcome Upon Approval. Maximum adult weight is 25 pounds. Call office for details. Leasing Hours ... Mon - Fri: 8:00 AM - 5:00 PM Call us at show contact info Our Location ..... 18520 8th Ave NW Shoreline, WA 98177 Website: www.lease-apts.com?n=highlands_west_shoreline&rp=vYFNwXQNAN89&t=wb Online Application: www.lease-apts.com?n=highlands_west_shoreline&rp=vYFNwXQNAN89&t=ap Schedule a Tour: www.lease-apts.com?n=highlands_west_shoreline&rp=vYFNwXQNAN89&t=sch All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY 884L00EL2DKJDO7",
