        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post The Retreat at Bothell Featured Floorplan: 3-bed / 2-bath / 1138 sq ft Monthly Price: $3225 - $8525 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Deposit: Call Call us today at show contact info Description: We Care Where You Live! From pristine mountain views to big-city adventures minutes away, your home at The Retreat at Bothell offers easy access to everywhere you want to be in King County. Additionally, our prime location near Woodinville Town Center means many of your favorite attractions are within easy reach. When the sun's shining, get your steps in at nearby Wilmot Gateway Park, or grab some friends for an afternoon of wine tasting in Woodinville. Whether you're traveling for work or play, you'll also love our community's convenient proximity to downtown Bellevue. Ready to experience it all for yourself? Reach out to schedule a tour of our luxury apartments today. Special Offer: Lease today and receive up to $500 off move in on select apartments. Plus enter to win a Roku Smart TV. While Supplies Last. Restrictions may Apply. Lease Terms: Call Pet Policy: Cats - allowed Dogs - allowed Apartment Amenities: − *High Ceilings (Top Floor Homes Only) − Cable Ready − Ceiling Fan − Dishwasher − Disposal − Hardwood Floors − Large Closets − Microwave − Patio/Balcony − Washer/Dryer Community Features: − Basketball Court − BBQ/Picnic Area − Clubhouse − Courtyard − Fitness Center − Free Weights − Internet Cafe − Media Room − Racquetball Court − Short Term Lease − Indoor Swimming Pool − On-Site Maintenance − On-Site Management − Outdoor Swimming Pool − Package Locker Room Address: 18101 126th Ave NE Bothell, WA 98011 Call us today at show contact info Mon - Fri: 9:00 AM - 6:00 PM Sat - Sun: 10:00 AM - 5:00 PM Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/retreatatbothell Website: www.lease-apts.com?n=retreat_at_bothell&rp=kA4zPUXtG3qb&t=wb Online Application: www.lease-a