        "info": "QR Code Link to This Post Welcome to 12th Avenue Arts! 1660 12th Avenue Seattle, WA 98122 Call us for more information! show contact info Rental Size: 1 BR - 1 BA - 588 sq ft Monthly Price: $1550 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Lease Length: 12-Month 12th Avenue Arts features 88 affordable apartments, performing arts space, community meeting space, and local retail - all under one roof at 12th and Pine on Capitol Hill. Residents at 12th Avenue Arts enjoy bright, naturally lit apartments, dishwashers in apartment, laundry on every floor, several spacious off-street community patios, and controlled building access. Two theaters and multiple retail stores and restaurants are available in the building for the residents' and neighborhood's enjoyment. The second floor commercial space also houses the main offices of Community Roots Housing. Our community features: ➢ Bike storage ➢ Community patios ➢ Controlled access ➢ Elevator ➢ On-site laundry ➢ Pet friendly ➢ Resident lounge ➢ Resident Services available ➢ Retail or restaurants in building ➢ Shared courtyard Our apartment features: ➢ Dishwasher ➢ Large windows Call us for more information! -- show contact info -- Our Pet-Policy: Pets as well as emotional support, companion, and service animals are allowed in all Community Roots Housing buildings. Some restrictions may apply to certain types of pets. Site managers can answer detailed questions about pet restrictions. Website: www.lease-apts.com?n=12th_avenue_arts&rp=hTBbsFhwJ83p&t=wb Online Application: www.lease-apts.com?n=12th_avenue_arts&rp=hTBbsFhwJ83p&t=ap All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY TOBBM71CT6OSEM",
