        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Welcome home to Polaris at Covington! Located at: 17110 SE 276th Street Covington, WA 98042 Rental Information: # of Bedrooms: 2 # of Bathrooms: 2 Square Footage: 905 sq ft Monthly Price: $2138 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Call us today! show contact info Cozy Comfort in Covington At Polaris at Covington, we know life is dynamic and spirited. That's why we've ensured that all our residents have access to the best amenities to accompany them. Impress your friends and host at our Movie theater with Stadium seating, or take advantage of our game room with a shuffleboard and a pool table! Here, you can experience a whole night out right at your doorstep. Give us a call today or schedule a tour! Let us show you why Polaris at Covington in Washington is the place to be. Community Features: ❖ Clubroom With Kitchen and Sitting Area ❖ Controlled Access Building ❖ Elevators ❖ Fitness Center ❖ Game Room with Shuffle Board and Pool Table. ❖ Garage Parking Available ❖ Playground ❖ Smoke Free Community ❖ Stadium Seating Movie Theater ❖ Storage Available Apartment Home Features: ❖ Built-in Microwave ❖ Deck or Balcony with Each Home ❖ Full Size Washer and Dryer ❖ Fully Equipped Kitchen with Black Appliances ❖ Large Closets ❖ New Construction Office Hours: Mon - Fri: 9:00 AM - 6:00 PM Sat: 10:00 AM - 5:00 PM Sun: - Call us today! show contact info Pet Policy: Pet deposit is $300 per pet. Non Refundable pet fee is $300 per pet. Monthly pet rent of $25 will be charged per pet. Leasing Options: 6-Month, 11-Month, 12-Month Website: www.apt-rental.com?n=polaris_at_covington&rp=c68gPMD82asY&t=wb Online Application: www.apt-rental.com?n=polaris_at_covington&rp=c68gPMD82asY&t=ap Schedule a Tour: www.apt-rental.com?n=polaris_at_covington&rp=c68gPMD82asY&t=sch All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY 75121BB15F504AAE",
