        "info": "QR Code Link to This Post Polaris at Covington Bedroom: 2 | Bathroom: 2 Square Footage: 905 sq ft Monthly Price: $2138 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Call us at show contact info Community Description Cozy Comfort in Covington At Polaris at Covington, we know life is dynamic and spirited. That's why we've ensured that all our residents have access to the best amenities to accompany them. Impress your friends and host at our Movie theater with Stadium seating, or take advantage of our game room with a shuffleboard and a pool table! Here, you can experience a whole night out right at your doorstep. Give us a call today or schedule a tour! Let us show you why Polaris at Covington in Washington is the place to be. Community Amenities ➢ Business Center ➢ Clubroom With Kitchen and Sitting Area ➢ Controlled Access Building ➢ Elevators ➢ Fitness Center ➢ Game Room with Shuffle Board and Pool Table. ➢ Garage Parking Available ➢ Playground ➢ Smoke Free Community ➢ Storage Available Apartment Features ➢ Built-in Microwave ➢ Deck or Balcony with Each Home ➢ Full Size Washer and Dryer ➢ Fully Equipped Kitchen with Black Appliances ➢ Large Closets ➢ New Construction Contact Information Visit Us: 17110 SE 276th Street Covington, WA 98042 Call us at show contact info Hours: Mon - Fri: 9:00 AM - 6:00 PM Sat: 10:00 AM - 5:00 PM Sun: - Website: www.rentalsapts.com?n=polaris_at_covington&rp=agfUtUCEocPv&t=wb Online Application: www.rentalsapts.com?n=polaris_at_covington&rp=agfUtUCEocPv&t=ap Schedule a Tour: www.rentalsapts.com?n=polaris_at_covington&rp=agfUtUCEocPv&t=sch Additional Details Pet Policy: Pet deposit is $300 per pet. Non Refundable pet fee is $300 per pet. Monthly pet rent of $25 will be charged per pet. Lease Terms: 6-Month, 11-Month, 12-Month All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY 75121BB15F504AAE",
