        "msg": "QR Code Link to This Post -- Village on Main Apartments -- Office Phone: show contact info $1,500 off if leased by 6/30/26!* *RESTRICTIONS APPLY. CONTACT US FOR DETAILS. Monthly Price: $3090 - $3162 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Apartment: 2 Bedroom | 2 Bathroom Square Footage: 1103 sq ft Waterfront living offers opportunity to bike, walk, or run along the bay, or to nearby Point Defiance Park. Our convenient covered parking garage keeps your car protected from the elements and offers peace of mind. Our furry residents will love to call Village on Main home - with plenty of open space to roam and pet-catered amenities! Pet Policy: Dogs and cats are welcome at our community. All pet residents must have their health check, shots and be spayed or neutered upon move-in. A signed Animal Addendum is required to be on file at our leasing office. Two (2) max pets allowed and breed restriction! Check out our beautiful community featuring: ◾ Along the Point Ruston Waterwalk ◾ Bike storage ◾ Controlled-entry access ◾ Landscaped courtyard with outdoor seating ◾ Pet friendly ◾ State-of-the-art fitness center ◾ 50 onsite retail with unique eateries and shopping right at your doorstep ◾ Package locker with 24/7 access to packages ◾ Private parking garage with direct access elevators ◾ Resident social lounge with demonstration kitchen and pool table ◾ Virtual Moving Concierge: Complimentary address change, set up home services and digital moving announcements ◾ Worry-free 24-hour onsite maintenance Apartment features include: ◾ 9-foot ceilings ◾ Elevator access ◾ Furnished apartments available ◾ In-home washer and dryer ◾ Oversized walk-in closets ◾ Private balcony or patio ◾ Separate dining area ◾ Wood-style plank flooring ◾ Air conditioning with programmable remote thermostat ◾ Breakfast bar with pendant lighting ◾ Expansive bay windows with 2-inch wood blinds ◾ Income Qualified Apartment Home (MFTE) ◾ Panoramic views of South Puget Sound, the Olympic Mountains, and Mount Rainier ◾ Polished kitchen countertops ◾ Stainless steel appliances including built-in microwave, refrigerator, and dishwasher Office Phone: show contact info Mon - Tue: 9:00 AM - 6:00 PM Wed: 12:00 PM - 6:00 PM Thu - Fri: 9:00 AM - 6:00 PM Sat: 10:00 AM - 5:00 PM Appointment scheduled preferred Website: www.lease-apts.com?n=village_on_main&rp=3CN7SVpjYhda&t=wb Online Application: www.lease-apts.com?n=village_on_main&rp=3CN7SVpjYhda&t=ap 5020 Main St Ruston, WA 98407 Lease Terms: 3-Month, 4-Month, 5-Month, 6-Month, 7-Month, 8-Month, 9-Month, 10-Month, 11-Month, 12-Month, 13-Month We only rent our apartments directly through our website or leasing office. We do not use any electronic funds transferring apps such as Zelle, Venmo, or Cashapp. All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY SMBAJ7ME0JAA6GC",
