        "info": "QR Code Link to This Post Vue 22 Apartments 2170 Bel-Red Rd Bellevue, WA 98052 Monthly Price: $3802 - $3893 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Bedrooms: 2 Bathrooms: 2 Square Footage: 1213 sq ft Contact us for more information! show contact info 4-weeks free! Features in this apartment home: ● Built-in desk- in select units ● Built-in linen closet- in select units ● Elevator access ● Oversized walk-in closets- in select units ● Polished quartz countertops ● Private balcony or patio- in select units ● Separate dining area- in select units ● Smart thermostat- in select units ● Wood-style plank flooring ● Ceiling fans in bedrooms- in select units ● Floor to ceiling double pane windows- in select units ● Front-loading washer and dryer ● Keyless smart lock technology ● Kitchen island with pendant lighting- in select units ● Mosaic tile kitchen backsplash ● Stainless steel appliances including built-in microwave, refrigerator, and dishwasher ● USB charging outlets in kitchen About the community: Our carefully crafted interiors boast state-of-the-art fixtures, plus stainless steel kitchen appliances, luxury quartz countertops, oversized walk-in closets in the bedroom, and wood-style flooring. Convenience comes standard with open-style, spacious layouts, full-size washer and dryer, onsite concierge, and built-in desks- perfect for working from home. Depending on the floor plan you select, your apartment may also have a private balcony or patio. No matter what your needs, no matter what floor plan you choose, we can't think of a better place to come home to and take in the view. We invite you to visit Vue 22 Apartments, ideally located in the Bellevue-Redmond Corridor, and see firsthand what sets us apart. Contact us today to schedule a tour. Amenities at our property: ● Controlled-entry access parking garage ● Co-working lounge with complimentary Wi-Fi ● Dog run ● Dog wash and self-service grooming area ● Onsite storage available ● Controlled-access bike storage and bike repair room ● Easy access to WA-520, I-90, I-405, and I-5 ● Live King County Metro transit screen in mail room lobby ● Multi-level fitness center with yoga studio and state-of-the-art equipment ● Open green space with bocce ball and oversized chess ● Resident social lounge with demonstration kitchen and billiards table, shuffleboard table and arcade games ● Rooftop deck featuring outdoor television, barbecue pavilion and outdoor fireplace ● Virtual moving concierge - Complimentary address change, set up home services and digital moving announcements Additional information: Contact us for more information! show contact info Terms: 12-Month, 13-Month, 14-Month, 15-Month Pets: Dogs and cats are welcome at our community. All pet residents must have their health check, shots and be spayed or neutered upon move-in. A signed Animal Addendum is required to be on file at our leasing office. Two (2) max pets allowed. Website: www.apts-rental.com?n=vue_22&rp=h9DmkwguiFgt&t=wb Online Application: www.apts-rental.com?n=vue_22&rp=h9DmkwguiFgt&t=ap We only rent our apartments directly through our website or leasing office. We do not use any electronic funds transferring apps such as Zelle, Venmo, or Cashapp. Images are representative of the property's finishes and layout; actual unit details may vary. All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY 4BD484BF352841E",
