        "info": "QR Code Link to This Post Africatown Plaza Located at: 1100 23rd Ave Seattle, WA 98122 Featured apartment home: Efficiency bed | 1 bath | 325 sq ft Monthly Price: $1325 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Reach out via phone: show contact info In the heart of Seattle's Central District, a renaissance is taking place. Africatown Plaza is a symbol of resurgence in this historically Black community, challenging years of displacement and disenfranchisement. A collaborative effort between Africatown Community Land Trust and Community Roots Housing, Africatown Plaza welcomes community members back into the African diaspora's historic home in Seattle. Wonderful Amenities! ◾ Community Amenities Coming Soon! Apartment Features! ◾ Apartment Amenities Coming Soon! ◾ Apartment Amenities Coming Soon! Hours: Mon - Fri: 8:00 AM - 5:00 PM Reach out via phone: show contact info Website: www.apt-rental.com?n=africatown_plaza&rp=tLp3K8eks6Ff&t=wb Online Application: www.apt-rental.com?n=africatown_plaza&rp=tLp3K8eks6Ff&t=ap Terms: 12-Month Pet Policy: Please call our Leasing Office for complete Pet Policy information. Pet Care: No. All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY TIC0XEE902JME2",
