        "msg": "QR Code Link to This Post Linden Flats 13280 Linden Ave N Seattle, WA 98133 Monthly Price: $1899 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Bedrooms: 2 Bathrooms: 2 Square Footage: 791 sq ft Call us today! show contact info Features in this apartment home: ◾ Dishwasher and Washer/Dryer in each unit ◾ Large windows that maximize natural light ◾ LED lighting with pendants over kitchen island ◾ Modern cabinets with soft close hinges ◾ Plush carpet in bedrooms ◾ Quartz countertops ◾ Two finish schemes ◾ Wide plank wood-look vinyl flooring About the community: Experience top-tier community amenities at our affordable community of Linden Flats in Seattle, WA. Your pet can enjoy its own amenity in a bark park designed just for them. Our dedicated on-site leasing and management team is here to answer your questions and provide a personalized tour of our welcoming community. Amenities at our property: ◾ Bike storage room with fully equipped bike repair station ◾ Clubhouse ◾ Community room with full kitchen, dining area for 10, TV and lounge ◾ Courtyard ◾ Fitness Center ◾ Fitness center with with yoga studio ◾ Game room with shuffle board, TV and lounge seating ◾ Garage parking available ◾ Gated Access ◾ On-site storage available ◾ Additional lounge area with gas fire pit ◾ Gas BBQ grilling stations ◾ Internet ◾ Lush, landscaped seating area ◾ Outdoor dining space ◾ Package Receiving ◾ Professional Management ◾ Turf lawn and play area ◾ Washer and Dryer in Home Additional information: Call us today! show contact info Terms: 12-Month Pets: Pets Welcome Upon Approval. Breed restrictions apply. Breed Restrictions: Pit Bulls, Rottweilers, Presa Canario, German Shepherds, Huskies, Malamutes, Dobermans, Chowchows, St. Bernard's, Great Danes, Akitas, Terriers(Staffordshire), American Bull Dog, Karelian Bear Dog, or Any Hybrid or Mix breed of one of the aforementioned breeds. Pet Amenities: Bark Park Website: www.lease-apts.com?n=linden_flats&rp=9DLpRjEkJhYL&t=wb Online Application: www.lease-apts.com?n=linden_flats&rp=9DLpRjEkJhYL&t=ap Schedule a Tour: www.lease-apts.com?n=linden_flats&rp=9DLpRjEkJhYL&t=sch Income Restrictions for Linden Flats # Occupants   -   Max Income       1 Person   -   $69,060       2 People   -   $78,960       3 People   -   $88,800       4 People   -   $98,640       5 People   -   $106,560       6 People   -   $114,480       7 People   -   $122,340 To qualify, annual income must be equal or below those in the chart, based on the total number of occupants. Contact the leasing office for more information. All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY VNH4C8DZMJJX4D",
