        "info": "QR Code Link to This Post Community Location: 13280 Linden Ave N - Seattle, WA 98133 Monthly Price: $1999 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Apartment Details: 3 Bedroom 2 Bath | 960 sq ft Leasing Options: 12-Month Call Today! show contact info Apartment Amenities: ❖ Dishwasher and Washer/Dryer in each unit ❖ Large windows that maximize natural light ❖ LED lighting with pendants over kitchen island ❖ Modern cabinets with soft close hinges ❖ Plush carpet in bedrooms ❖ Quartz countertops ❖ Two finish schemes ❖ Wide plank wood-look vinyl flooring Property Features: ❖ Bike storage room with fully equipped bike repair station ❖ Clubhouse ❖ Community room with full kitchen, dining area for 10, TV and lounge ❖ Courtyard ❖ Fitness Center ❖ Fitness center with with yoga studio ❖ Game room with shuffle board, TV and lounge seating ❖ Garage parking available ❖ Gated Access ❖ On-site storage available ❖ Additional lounge area with gas fire pit ❖ Gas BBQ grilling stations ❖ Internet ❖ Lush, landscaped seating area ❖ Outdoor dining space ❖ Package Receiving ❖ Professional Management ❖ Turf lawn and play area ❖ Washer and Dryer in Home Description: You'll find all of Seattle's best attractions within about ten minutes of Linden Flats, including Pike Place Market, the Great Seattle Wheel, and the Space Needle. Every weekend is an adventure in cuisine, culture, and fun. Seattle's bike-friendly streets, hiking trails, beaches, lakes, and nearby mountains beckon locals to magnificent outdoor recreation year-round. Bitter Lake has it all, earning an excellent reputation for its schools, nightlife, and diversity. The neighborhood's namesake lake is stocked with fish, making it a favorite weekend destination. Many of the area's local businesses have served the area for decades, contributing to the unique sense of community here. Pets: Pets Welcome Upon Approval. Breed restrictions apply. Breed Restrictions: Pit Bulls, Rottweilers, Presa Canario, German Shepherds, Huskies, Malamutes, Dobermans, Chowchows, St. Bernard's, Great Danes, Akitas, Terriers(Staffordshire), American Bull Dog, Karelian Bear Dog, or Any Hybrid or Mix breed of one of the aforementioned breeds. Pet Amenities: Bark Park Call Today! show contact info Website: www.rentalsapts.com?n=linden_flats&rp=uiGY7Ntb27Dx&t=wb Online Application: www.rentalsapts.com?n=linden_flats&rp=uiGY7Ntb27Dx&t=ap Schedule a Tour: www.rentalsapts.com?n=linden_flats&rp=uiGY7Ntb27Dx&t=sch Income Restrictions for Linden Flats # Occupants   -   Max Income       1 Person   -   $69,060       2 People   -   $78,960       3 People   -   $88,800       4 People   -   $98,640       5 People   -   $106,560       6 People   -   $114,480       7 People   -   $122,340 To qualify, annual income must be equal or below those in the chart, based on the total number of occupants. Contact the leasing office for more information. All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY 5EIST6TXN7RTJEC",
