        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Monthly Price: $3199 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. SIZE: 1089 sq ft | BEDROOMS: 2 | BATHROOMS: 2 LEASE TERMS: 3-Month, 4-Month, 5-Month, 6-Month, 7-Month, 8-Month, 9-Month, 10-Month, 11-Month, 12-Month Contact Info: show contact info ABOUT COMMUNITY: Have you been looking for immaculate apartment home living in Seattle, WA? Congratulations, you've found it! The Shelby offers all the comforts of home in a pristine setting that is second to none. Our apartment community is nestled in the heart of Seattle, Washington, where everything you love is just a short drive away. We are ideally located right around the corner from local shopping, dining, and entertainment. It's time to pamper yourself with the lifestyle you deserve! Schedule a Tour: https://www.theshelby.com/?utm_knock=cl&doorway=schedule Pet Policy: Life is PAWSOME here. Relax in comfort with your furry friend at your side! Pets Welcome Upon Approval. Breed restrictions apply. Limit of 2 pets per home. Pet deposit is $250 per pet. Monthly pet rent of $50 will be charged per pet. APARTMENT FEATURES: ● Cable Ready ● Ceiling Fans ● Den in Select Units ● Dining Room ● Dishwasher ● Disposal ● Heating ● Microwave ● Range ● Wi-Fi ● Carpeted Floors ● Eat-in Kitchen ● French Doors in Select Units ● Granite Countertops ● Hardwood Floors ● High Speed Internet Access ● Refrigerator ● Walk-In Closets ● Washer and Dryer in Home ● Window Coverings COMMUNITY FEATURES: ● Bike Racks ● Clubhouse ● Courtyard ● Elevator ● Lounge ● Package Service ● Sundeck ● Butterfly MX Video Callbox ● Conference Center with Wi-Fi ● Controlled Access ● Laundry Facilities ● Luxer One Package Lockers ● Maintenance on site ● Picnic Area With Barbecue ● State-of-the-art Fitness Center CONTACT US TODAY! The Shelby 2201 4th Ave Seattle, WA 98121 Mon - Fri: 9:00 AM - 6:00 PM Contact Info: show contact info Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/theshelbyapartments Website: www.lease-apts.com?n=shelby&rp=kgf3t5EH2hWV&t=wb Online Application: www.lease-apts.com?n=shelby&rp=kgf3t5EH2hWV&t=ap Schedule a Tour: www.lease-apts.com?n=shelby&rp=kgf3t5EH2hWV&t=sch Availability and pricing are subject to change daily All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY IIK0BRADV47KE1",
