ome Upon Approval. Deposit: $225 Refundable and $225 Non-Refundable Pet Fee $20 per pet per month Breed restrictions apply. Limit of 2 pets per home. 35 lbs. weight restrictions Call us at show contact info Website: www.rentalsapts.com?n=foster_commons&rp=qmhxnLa2qkZR&t=wb Online Application: www.rentalsapts.com?n=foster_commons&rp=qmhxnLa2qkZR&t=ap Schedule a Tour: www.rentalsapts.com?n=foster_commons&rp=qmhxnLa2qkZR&t=sch All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY 52VK5OMH1ZIS1N2A",
