        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Welcome to Polaris at Eastgate! 13300 SE Eastgate Way Bellevue, WA 98005 Text or call for details at show contact info Rental Size: 3 BR - 2 BA - 1170 sq ft Monthly Price: $2350 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Lease Length: 6-Month **AFFORDABLE HOUSING - INCOME RESTRICTIONS APPLY!!** Nestled in the vibrant city of Bellevue, Washington, Polaris at Eastgate enjoys a prime location that seamlessly blends urban conveniences with natural beauty. Positioned in the heart of Eastgate, residents have easy access to a diverse array of shopping, dining, and entertainment options within the lively Bellevue area. The community is strategically situated for commuters, with proximity to major highways and public transportation hubs, facilitating effortless travel to downtown Bellevue and beyond. Against the backdrop of the picturesque Pacific Northwest landscape, Polaris at Eastgate provides a tranquil and inviting setting, creating an ideal home for those seeking a dynamic and well-connected lifestyle. Our community features: ✓ Business Center ✓ Early Learning Center ✓ Elevator ✓ Game Room ✓ Online Services ✓ On-site Interior Bike Storage ✓ Onsite Storage Available ✓ Parking: $175/month MAX 1 Parking Space with Limited Availability ✓ Recycling ✓ Resident Services ✓ Easy Access to Transit, Retail, & Shopping ✓ Game Room ✓ Internet Cafe ✓ Minutes from I-90, I-405 and Downtown Bellevue ✓ Non-smoking Community ✓ Preventative Health Support ✓ Some Paid Utilities Include: Water, Sewer, and Garbage ✓ State-of-the-art Fitness Center ✓ Translation Service Available ✓ Underground Parking Available Our apartment features: ✓ Cable Ready ✓ Dishwasher ✓ Hardwood Style Floors ✓ Heating ✓ Microwave ✓ Oven ✓ Range ✓ Refrigerator ✓ Remarkable Views in Select Units ✓ Tub/Shower ✓ Full-Size Washer & Dryer ✓ Fully Equipped Kitchens with Stainless Steel Appliances ✓ Spacious Master Bedrooms With Walk-In Closets ✓ Stylish Studio, 1, 2 & 3 Bedroom Homes Text or call for details at -- show contact info -- Our Pet-Policy: Non-Refundable Pet Deposit: $400 / Pet Rent/Monthly: $40 2 Pets MAX Pets Welcome Upon Approval. Pet Restrictions: Pit Bulls, Rottweilers, Presa Canario, German Shepherds, Huskies, Malamutes, Dobermans, Chowchows, St. Bernards, Great Danes, Akitas, Terriers(Staffordshire), American Bull Dog, Karelian Bear Dog, or Any Hybrid or Mix breed of one of the aforementioned breeds. No Tarantulas or Piranhas, No Reptiles (snake, Iguanas, etc), No Ferrets, Skunks, Raccoons, Squirrels, Rabbits, Or Birds(Parrot, Cockatiels, Macaws) Website: www.rentalsapts.com?n=polaris_at_eastgate&rp=5d3KzjZSykvm&t=wb Income Restrictions for Polaris at Eastgate # Occupants   -   Max Income       1 Person   -   $66,000       2 People   -   $75,420       3 People   -   $84,840       4 People   -   $94,260       5 People   -   $101,820       6 People   -   $109,380       7 People   -   $116,940 To qualify, annual income must be equal or below those in the chart, based on the total number of occupants. Contact the leasing office for more information. All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY 1B8F2E86EAA24E",
