        "info": "QR Code Link to This Post Monthly Price: $3825 - $4050 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. SIZE: 1448 sq ft | BEDROOMS: 3 | BATHROOMS: 3 LEASE TERMS: 6-Month, 12-Month Call us today! show contact info ABOUT COMMUNITY: Convenient sophistication takes center stage at The Villas in Bellevue, the newest neighborhood in a vibrant city. Step outside to Lake Hills Village, a plaza that offers every convenience. Dining, shopping, and more await you at every turn. Your New Home Awaits! Well-appointed apartments for rent in Bellevue, WA. Features in this apartment home: ? Cable Ready ? Carpet ? Deck ? Dishwasher & Disposal ? Heating ? High Speed Internet Access ? Microwave ? Range ? Refrigerator ? Balcony/Patio ? Dining Room ? Oversized Closets ? Tub/Shower ? Vinyl Flooring ? Walk-In Closets ? Washer & dryer in home ? Window Coverings + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + Amenities at our property: ? Bicycle Storage ? Maintenance on site ? Property Manager on Site ? Renters Insurance Program ? Storage Space ? 24-Hour Fitness Center ? Lush, park like setting ? Minutes to I-90/I-405 ? On bus Route 271 ? Online Services ? Partnered With EPremiuminsurance.Com ? T-Mobile, Bellevue College within minutes ? Walking distance to schools & library + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + + About the community: Convenient sophistication takes center stage at The Villas in Bellevue, the newest neighborhood in a vibrant city. Step outside to Lake Hills Village, a plaza that offers every convenience. Dining, shopping, and more await you at every turn. Amplify your expectations with nearby Marymoor Park and their concert series. If you don't feel like leaving home sit back and be a part of our very own outdoor concert event just steps away in the Village Plaza Amphitheater. Enjoy your own private veranda, or spend time with friends at one of the many trendy locales in the Village Plaza. On those summer weekends don't forget the Farmer's Market; where you can pick up fresh, local produce. In your backyard, you will find a lush greenbelt where you can tour a cedar forest and learn about local wildlife. Pets: Pets Welcome Upon Approval. Please Call For Details. Office Phone: show contact info Hours: Mon - FRI: 9:00 AM - 5:00 PM Website: www.rentalsapts.com?n=villas_in_bellevue&rp=6g7n3del5y&t=wb Schedule a Tour: www.rentalsapts.com?n=villas_in_bellevue&rp=6g7n3del5y&t=sch All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY Pet Policy: Pets Welcome Upon Approval. Please Call For Details. APARTMENT FEATURES: ❖ Cable Ready ❖ Carpet ❖ Deck ❖ Dishwasher & Disposal ❖ Heating ❖ High Speed Internet Access ❖ Microwave ❖ Range ❖ Refrigerator ❖ Balcony/Patio ❖ Dining Room ❖ Oversized Closets ❖ Tub/Shower ❖ Vinyl Flooring ❖ Walk-In Closets ❖ Washer & dryer in home ❖ Window Coverings COMMUNITY FEATURES: ❖ Bicycle Storage ❖ Maintenance on site ❖ Property Manager on Site ❖ Renters Insurance Program ❖ Storage Space ❖ 24-Hour Fitness Center ❖ Lush, park like setting ❖ Minutes to I-90/I-405 ❖ On bus Route 271 ❖ Online Services ❖ Partnered With EPremiuminsurance.Com ❖ T-Mobile, Bellevue College within minutes ❖ Walking distance to schools & library CONTACT US TODAY! Villas in Bellevue 595 156th Ave SE Bellevue, WA 98007 Mon - Fri: 9:00 AM - 5:00 PM Call us today! show contact info Website: www.leaseaptsnow.com?n=villas_in_bellevue&rp=k1swi8hZ2YBJ&t=wb Online Application: www.leaseaptsnow.com?n=villas_in_bellevue&rp=k1swi8hZ2YBJ&t=ap Schedule a Tour: www.leaseaptsnow.com?n=villas_in_bellevue&rp=k1swi8hZ2YBJ&t=sch All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY SE61L3MTEAX1M2A",
