        "msg": "QR Code Link to This Post Copper Gate Visit Our Community Today! 4798 Auburn Way North Auburn, WA 98002 Call us today! show contact info Relaxation and recreation are at the forefront, with an indoor fitness center, outdoor pool, splash pad, and a cyber café available to all residents. We are pet-friendly, too, so your four-legged friends can roam around the neighborhood. As a resident of Copper Gate in Auburn, WA, stunning landscapes, thoughtful amenities, and extraordinary services will make each day a delight. Bedrooms: 4 | Bathrooms: 2 Square Footage: 1309 sq ft Please call Our Residents Enjoy: − Basketball Court − Business Center − Community Garden Nursery − Cyber Cafe − Horseshoes − Indoor Gymnasium − Indoor Playground − On-site Bike Repair − Outdoor Barbecues − Pet Friendly − 16 Buildings and 1 Clubhouse − 4 Outdoor Playgrounds − Courtesy Patrol − Easy Access to Nearby Farmers Market − Garages and Carports Available − Indoor State-of-the-art Fitness Center − Nearby Walking Trails − Outdoor Sports Court − Picnic Shelter with Tables − Shimmering Swimming Pool and Splash Pad This Apartment Home Comes With: − Balcony and Patio − Black Appliances − Carpeted Floors in Bedrooms − Ceiling Fans − Full-size Washer and Dryer in Home − Fully-equipped Kitchen − Large Closets − Microwave − Patio − Spacious Bedrooms − Business Center − Clubhouse − Fitness Center − Garage − Playground − Pool Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/coppergateapartments Website: www.leaseaptsnow.com?n=copper_gate&rp=uezwk3CuGSrt&t=wb Online Application: www.leaseaptsnow.com?n=copper_gate&rp=uezwk3CuGSrt&t=ap Schedule a Tour: www.leaseaptsnow.com?n=copper_gate&rp=uezwk3CuGSrt&t=sch Call us today! show contact info Pet-Policy: Pets Welcome Upon Approval. Breed restrictions apply. Limit of 2 pets per home. Non-refundable pet fee is $400 per pet. Monthly pet rent of $25 will be charged per pet. Lease-Length: 6-Month Call for Directions All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY S8M3ODVSB2ZINB7",
