        "info": "QR Code Link to This Post Redmond Square 7797 170th Ave NE Redmond, WA 98052 Contact: show contact info RECEIVE BETWEEN $1250-$5000 FREE ON SELECT APARTMENT HOMES Restrictions apply. Reach out to our team for more information. . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . Rental Size: 2 BR - 2 BA - 886 - 1097 sq ft Monthly Price: $2700 - $3550 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Lease Length: 9-Month, 12-Month . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . Tucked away in the heart of Redmond, Washington, you will find the epitome of apartment home living enjoyment. Welcome to Redmond Square, the perfect place to live if you want equally excellent amenities and location. Easy access to Interstate 405 and WA-520 means you will never have to travel far for shopping, entertainment, and daily needs. . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . Features and Amenities: ✓ Bicycle Storage ✓ Controlled Access ✓ Courtyard ✓ Grill ✓ Two Fitness Rooms ✓ Two Terraces ✓ Hearing Impaired Accessible ✓ Recycling ✓ Renters Insurance Program ✓ Reserved Parking . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . This Apartment Home Comes With: ✓ Cable Ready ✓ Carpet in bedrooms ✓ City Views ✓ Dishwasher ✓ Expansive Windows ✓ Granite Countertops ✓ Heating ✓ High Speed Internet Access ✓ Large Closets ✓ Vinyl Flooring ✓ Microwave ✓ Oven/Range ✓ Private Patio ✓ Refrigerator/Freezer ✓ Smoke Free ✓ Storage Space ✓ Tub/Shower ✓ Vaulted Ceiling ✓ Washer and Dryer ✓ Wheelchair Accessible (Rooms) . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . Contact: -- show contact info -- Website: www.apt-rental.com?n=redmond_square&rp=1S1Y85pbSXRe&t=wb Online Application: www.apt-rental.com?n=redmond_square&rp=1S1Y85pbSXRe&t=ap Schedule a Tour: www.apt-rental.com?n=redmond_square&rp=1S1Y85pbSXRe&t=sch Pets: Pets Welcome Upon Approval. Please Call For Details. . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY MZ6BAV04LHZD4XZ",
